Unified Inbox – All Your Mail Accounts in One Email App
Supporting IMAP, POP3 as well as Exchange protocols. TypeApp automatically configures them once you sign in. View & sync all your email accounts from one Unified Inbox, while enjoying lightning fast true push email.

People-Centric – Bringing People Together
Communicating with people is important and with TypeApp’s innovative people-centric features, it becomes even more simple. Focus on mail from people much faster with the People Switch, or be notified when specific VIP Notifications.

Group Mail – Quick & Easy Mailing
You can create a Shared Group with all your contacts at your work and personal accounts, which every member can view, to receive and send emails.

Simplifying Email with Clusters
Automatically combine relevant emails into a single expanding slot using TypeApp smart Clusters as well as set different notification sounds for specific services. With Clusters, you can control all emails from a specific sender and with multi-edit quickly moving, deleting, or marking clusters as spam is simple.

FEATURE RICH EXPERIENCE
● Instant, Smart Push Notifications - Quiet Hours, Custom Sounds, Vibrate, LED Light, Snooze Alerts and other preferences per each of your accounts
● Smart Conversations – Makes mail app convenient and easy
● Rich Text - Easily configure text styles and add your logo
● Calendar Sync and Contacts – Get your ActiveSync work account in sync
● Android Wear - Intelligent email on your wrist
● Configurable Menus – Customize your menus with actions that really matter to you
● Wireless Printing – Integrated with any supported printer
● Days to Sync – Saves memory for offline use
● Unread and Scrollable Widgets - Access your mails inbox at a glance
● Beautiful Dark Mode & Themes
● Account Color Coding - Know from which account a mail has been received

Getting Stuff Done
Quickly mark emails that you wish to be handled later & set yourself reminders. When you finish handling an email, you can simply mark it done and get it out of your way without having to delete the email. Use our Smart Filters to easily filter emails by unread/starred.

Visually Appealing – Beautifully Designed
Easily recognize popular services by their icons and give your friends and contacts an avatar photo to help you process your incoming mail faster. Quickly see how many unread emails are in your inbox with the TypeApp icon (for supported devices) or with the 1x1 unread widget for any account of your accounts including the Unified Inbox. Set colors for your accounts to help them stand out or use TypeApp’s automatic Dark Theme which switches per the daylight hours in your area.

Security – Private & Secured
TypeApp takes your security and privacy seriously by utilizing industry leading encryption. You can rest easy knowing your data is always encrypted to protect all your email communications and keep your information secured. With passcode and lock screen, you can set a timed lock screen to protect your private emails, or use SMS verification to ensure your email app is safe.

We ❤ getting your feedback! Please e mail us anytime: support@typeapp.com with any questions or suggestions you may have!

title: Trentino VR - Virtual Reality
description:
With Trentino VR you can live highly immersive experiences, even from your own sofa. Virtual reality can take you to amazing locations, making you the protagonist of stories that develop around you, in a 360 degrees view.

Go hiking in the Dolomites, enjoy gorgeous meals in unique locations in the mountains, relax in a Spa or at the Swimming Pool, ride a scooter among the vineyards, admire the sunrise from a mountain hut and try out sports like paragliding, snowboarding, climbing, trekking, paddleboarding, canoeing and more.

Trentino VR has gathered for you the best experiences that this territory can offer, you just have to choose how to live them. The app offers 2 viewing modes: 360 or VR, the latter needs a virtual reality viewer that you can use with your smartphone. VR is the best option to get a complete immersion in your chosen experience. If you do not have a viewer you can request it here: www.trentinovr.com.
Trentino VR currently collects 26 experiences from 8 territories and will be constantly updated with new content.

Download the app, select the territory you want to know more about and then choose the experience you want to live.

Trentino VR is an innovative app and as such it may not work properly on all devices. Any operating problems can be reported at info@trentinovr.com.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Make sure your phone is equipped with a gyroscope and accelerometer, essential features for the correct functioning not only of the Trentino VR app, but of all the virtual reality content that can be accessed via smartphones. These sensors allow the device to recognize even the smallest movements of the head and adapt the image accordingly, which otherwise appears steady.

In any case, any functioning problem can be reported to info@trentinovr.com.

Go hiking in the Dolomites, enjoy gorgeous meals in unique locations in the mountains, relax in a Spa or at the Swimming Pool, ride a scooter among the vineyards, admire the sunrise from a mountain hut and try out sports like paragliding, snowboarding, climbing, trekking, paddleboarding, canoeing and more.

Trentino VR has gathered for you the best experiences that this territory can offer, you just have to choose how to live them. The app offers 2 viewing modes: 360 or VR, the latter needs a virtual reality viewer that you can use with your smartphone. VR is the best option to get a complete immersion in your chosen experience. If you do not have a viewer you can request it here: www.trentinovr.com.
Trentino VR currently collects 26 experiences from 8 territories and will be constantly updated with new content.

Download the app, select the territory you want to know more about and then choose the experience you want to live.

title: ATV Pizza Bike Rider Delivery Boy
description:
Begin your adventure of being an ATV quad bike rider where you are playing the role of pizza delivery boy in town. Get ready to enjoy the fun adventure of both pizza delivery boy and atv quad bike rider that makes the best combination between the pizza delivery boy and atv quad bike rider games. Dare to drive against the real traffic challenging delivery missions. It will bring you fun while playing as atv quad bike rider pizza delivery boy role and explore the city town streets while delivering the delicious pizza. Try out this super cool bike rider pizza delivery game in town. 

Don't make the client wait for too long for his pizza which is delivered by your companies atv quad bike rider pizza delivery boy. Sit on your crazy atv quad bike because this pizza delivery ATV bike is designed for people who love to play the role of bike rider pizza delivery boy. Experience this amazing pizza delivery boy atv quad bike game which gives you the excitement of delivering pizza to different locations in limited time. So take your pizza delivery boy and get ready to deliver pizzas. Choose the shortest route to reach the destination which is marked by the pizza lover client.

Grab a chance to experience the amazing pizza delivery quad bike game, which gives you the excitement of delivering hot delicious pizzas to different locations on time as a professional pizza delivery bike rider. So become a pizza delivery duty boy and get ready to deliver pizzas with this ATV bike pizza delivery game. Work as fast-food delivery atv quad bike rider. Prove your atv quad bike riding skills as well as your professional skills by this atv quad bike pizza delivery game. Race your quad bike as a real atv rider and make your delivery safe without hitting other cars and vehicles that are coming in your way while you are reaching towards your destination.

Features:

-Complete the levels with different pizza delivery tasks.
-Reach the destination with in the limited time.
-Collect rewards on completing the levels.
-3D HD graphics with realistic city environment.
-Safely reach the destination with in the coming flow of the traffic.
-Fully operational pizza delivery service.
-Realistic animation with advance ATV physics.
-Earn money and unlock more faster ATV quad bike.

title: Polarsteps - Travel Planner & Tracker
description:
Polarsteps seuraa automaattisesti reittiäsi ja vierailemiasi paikkoja matkailusi aikana. Pidä vain puhelintasi taskussa, niin sovellus luo oman kauniin matkapäiväkirjasi.

Kun yhdistät internetiin, matkareittisi, sijaintisi ja valokuvasi siirtyvät saumattomasti henkilökohtaiseen matkaprofiiliisi ja värikkäälle maailmankartalle, jonka voit jakaa helposti läheistesi kesken. Matkasi päätteeksi voit tilata hetkessä kauniin tulostetun valokuva-albumin.

** OMINAISUUDET **

SEURAA REITTIÄSI
Jäljitä automaattisesti reittiäsi ja vierailemiasi paikkoja ilman, että otat puhelintasi pois taskusta.

SEURAA LÄHEISTESI MATKAA
Seuraa ystäviesi ja perheesi matkaa ja tunne olevasi heidän mukanaan.

VERTAILE MATKUSTUSTILASTOJASI
Näe yksityiskohtainen yhteenveto reitistäsi ja eläydy matkaasi uudelleen erilaisilla tilastoilla, kuten matkan kestolla, vierailtujen maiden määrällä ja matkan kokonaispituudella.

HANKI VALOKUVA-ALBUMI VÄLITTÖMÄSTI
Luo kaunis tulostettu valokuva-albumi, jossa on mukana matkustustietosi ja reittisi.

JÄLJITYS TOIMII OFFLINE-TILASSA
Jäljitä koko reittisi ilman verkkoyhteyttä. Sovellus synkronoi automaattisesti, kun yhdistät uudelleen verkkoon.

JAA HETKESI
Jäljitä matkaasi itseäsi varten tai jaa kokemuksesi seuraajiesi kesken Polarstepsissä ja sen ulkopuolella. Voit myös tehdä julkaisuja suoraan Instagramissa, Facebookissa, Whatsappissa ja muilla sosiaalisilla kanavilla.

VÄHÄINEN AKUN KULUTUS
Travel Tracker kuluttaa akkua vain 4 % tavallista enemmän, sillä sovellus määrittää sijaintisi älykkäällä teknologialla.

TÄYSI YKSITYISYYDEN HALLINTA
Seuraa matkojasi yksityisesti, jaa ne läheisten kesken kotona tai inspiroi kokonaista yhteisöä! Saat itse päättää, kuka näkee matkapäiväkirjasi tai matkustusblogisi.

EI VAADI TILIÄ
Ystäväsi voivat seurata matkaasi ilman tiliä. Jaa vain salainen matkalinkkisi heidän kanssaan, niin he voivat tutustua seikkailuihisi Polarsteps-sivustolla.

HAE INSPIRAATIOTA SEURAAVAN MATKASI SUUNNITTELUUN
Tutustu Staff Picks -suosituksiin tai käytä hakutoimintoa löytääksesi mitä inspiroivimpia matkoja ympäri maailman!


** SOVELLUS MEDIASSA ***

• "Polarsteps auttaa jäljittämään ja jakamaan matkoja helpolla ja visuaalisesti miellyttävällä tavalla." - The Next Web
• "Polarstepsilla luotava matkailuloki on vaikuttava, ja se saa lukijansa matkustusjalan vipattamaan." - TechCrunch
• "Polarsteps-sovellus korvaa matkapäiväkirjan ja tekee siitä helpomman ja kauniimman." - National Geographic


** PALAUTE **
Kuulemme mielellämme mielipiteemme Polarstepsista. Ole hyvä ja lähetä palautteesi (englanniksi) osoitteeseen support@polarsteps.com tai Facebookissa osoitteessa www.facebook.com/polarsteps.

title: Dna analyzer
description:
NOTE: We developed a new tool, called Dna toolkit. It is faster and offers more options!

Dna sequence analyzer is a tool which provides a user with an intuitive interface for basic sequence analysis. User can choose, whether he will input the sequence manually, or will he upload it via file explorer. Dna sequence analyzer then displays some basic statistics regarding the inputted sequence. This app is meant for everyone who always wished for a handy tool for quick insight into sequence structure. This version (1.0), provides support for DNA and RNA molecules, in further upgrades we will work  on protein files also.

NOTE: If the Analyser fails to load the file from internal memory, please download a file explorer.

Almost every aspect of the app is modifiable, so you can easily customize everything to your needs. • Voice recognition for super-fast input • Synchronisation between devices for joint editing • Manage multiple shopping lists with categories • Add quantity and price information to keep track of your purchases • Barcode scanner for quick input of known products • Import text from web pages, e.g. conveniently import recipes • Recipes can be saved separately to be quickly added to your shopping list when needed • Many options for font, size and color customization … and a lot more Have fun with this intuitive shopping list app. For questions or comments please contact us at: support@shopping-app.net
descriptionHTML:
An easy-to-use shopping list app. You can create your shopping lists directly by speaking. Possibility to create multiple lists. Almost every aspect of the app is modifiable, so you can easily customize everything to your needs.

• Voice recognition for super-fast input
• Synchronisation between devices for joint editing
• Manage multiple shopping lists with categories
• Add quantity and price information to keep track of your purchases
• Barcode scanner for quick input of known products
• Import text from web pages, e.g. conveniently import recipes
• Recipes can be saved separately to be quickly added to your shopping list when needed
• Many options for font, size and color customization

… and a lot more


Have fun with this intuitive shopping list app.

For questions or comments please contact us at: support@shopping-app.net

title: WeShare by MobilePay
description:
Helsingin Sanomien testivoittaja - kulujenjakamissovellukset, 21.5.2018

WeShare auttaa sinua ja kavereitasi erilaisten tapahtumien, esimerkiksi matkan tai juhlien suunnittelussa ja yhteisten kulujen kirjaamisessa.

Voitte jakaa ryhmän kesken kuvia, kuluja ja käydä keskustelua - kaikki tämä yhdessä sovelluksessa. WeShare pitää kirjaa siitä kuka on velkaa kenellekin ja näette aina yhteenvedon ryhmän kuluista ja omasta osuudestasi. Ja kun on kulujen tasaamisen aika, se onnistuu helposti MobilePaylla. 

WeSharen käyttö on maksutonta ja tarvitset vain suomalaisen puhelinnumeron. Rekisteröityminen sujuu todella nopeasti MobilePay-linkityksellä ja tietosi (nimi, sähköposti ja puhelinnumero) siirtyvät MobilePaysta suoraan WeShareen.

WeSharessa on mahdollista:
-              Luoda ryhmiä ja kutsua muita liittymään niihin
-              Jakaa kuluja, kuvia ja käydä keskusteluja ryhmän jäsenten kesken
-              Kun on kulujen tasauksen aika, niin maksaminen onnistuu helposti MobilePaylla. WeSharen käyttö onnistuu kuitenkin myös ilman MobilePay-linkitystä.
-              WeShareen pystyy lisäämään kustannuksia monilla eri valuutoilla ja niiden muuntaminen euroiksi käy vaivatta

title: Postinfo
description:
Postinfo     - Department Posts Android Mobile Application
Postinfo, the citizen centric android Mobile application of Department of Posts developed by Centre for Excellence in Postal Technology .The app   provides the following facilities; 
1)	Tracking
2)	Post office search
3)	Postage Calculator
4)	Insurance premium calculator
5)	Interest calculator
Brief description of each facility is given below;
TRACKING: 
The tracking facility is made available on this mobile app for the following types of mail items.
•	Speed Post		•	Registered Letter	•	Insured Letter
•	Value Payable Letter	•	Insured Value Payable Letter	•	Registered Packets
•	Registered Periodicals	•	Registered Parcel	•	Insured Parcel
•	Value Payable Parcel	•	Insured Value Payable Parcel	•	Business Parcel
•	Business Parcel COD	•	Express Parcel	•	Express Parcel COD
•	Electronic Money Order (e-MO)

	
The users can view the status of the above mentioned type of articles by entering the articles number and touching the Track button. The following additional facilities are also available.
•	Save the results for future reference 
•	Share it with others through Android native sharing apps viz. Bluetooth, WhatsApp, Facebook etc.
POST OFFICE SEARCH: 
By entering first three character of the name of the Post office or by entering the Pin code of the office the users can get a list of matching Post offices. By clicking again on the row the user gets the details like Name of Post office, Street address (location), contact details of the Post office (where ever available) for the selected Post office. The name of the Division and contact details.   

Offline Pincode search has feature to find  nearest post office, locating post office on Google Map and Making call to Post office

POSTAGE CALCULATOR:  
The app will calculate the Postage (tariff) based on the weight entered by the user for the following items.. 
•	Ordinary letter	•	Speed post Domestic *
•	Registered letter	•	Ordinary Parcel
•	Registered Parcel	•	Registered book packet
•	Registered book packet containing Printed books	•	Ordinary Registered book packet 
•	Ordinary book packet containing Printed books	•	Book packet containing periodicals
•	Book packet containing Registered News papers
•	*Domestic Speed Post Tariff depends on distance between place of origin and destination.   
•	Based on tariff there are 5 slabs of tariff viz. local, up to 200 KM, 201 to 1000 KM, and 1001 to 2000KM and above 2000KM.  The calculator shows the tariff for all categories)
PREMIUM CALCULATOR  
The Department is offering various types of Life Insurance Policies through Postal Life Insurance and Rural Postal Life Insurance. The users can check the premium payable for all the eligible types of Postal /Rural Postal Life insurance Policies on the basis of the input entered.
INTEREST CALCULATOR 
Post office is offering different types of Small Savings Schemes as mentioned below:
•	Sukanya Samriddhi yojaana	•	Recurring Deposit
•	Time Deposit (1 year, 2 year, 3 year and 5 year)	•	Monthly Income Scheme
•	Senior Citizen Savings Scheme	•	National Savings Certificate 
•	Kisan Vikas Patra

title: Kivra Sverige
description:
Var tredje svensk använder Kivra. Upplev lugnet med digitala brev och kvitton du med. 
Med Kivra får du viktig post digitalt. Istället för i vanliga brevlådan. Nu kan du även få kvitton i Kivra. Gratis, säkert och dessutom bra för miljön!

Vilken post kan du få i Kivra?
Slipp papper i brevlådan! I Kivra kan du få post såsom deklarationen, fakturor, kreditupplysningar och lönespecifikationer. Det enda du behöver göra är att registrera dig sedan får du automatiskt din post digitalt från myndigheter och anslutna företag du är kund hos. Snabbt, smidigt och sorterat!

Just nu skickar över 20 000 avsändare post via Kivra och nya avsändare ansluter sig dessutom löpande, vilket innebär att du successivt kommer få mer av din post digitalt.
 
Vilka kvitton kan du få i Kivra?
Kvitton i Kivra lanserades i februari 2020. Läs mer på kivra.se/kvitton

Betala fakturor med ett klick
Slipp krångla med med att skriva in betalningsmottagare, datum för betalning och belopp! Med Kivras betaltjänst kan du enkelt betala fakturor med ett klick. Du får en bra överblick över fakturan och kan sedan lägga in fakturan för betalning direkt i Kivra så att pengarna är mottagaren tillhanda på förfallodagen.

Post på dina villkor!
Du får en pushnotis när du får ny post i Kivra, var du än befinner dig. Är det någon avsändare du vill få papperspost från kan du välja att ställa av avsändaren som inloggad på Kivra under Inställningar.

Läs mer om Kivra på www.kivra.com

title: Яндекс (бета)
description: Станьте первыми, кто опробует новые возможности мобильного Яндекса – скачайте бета-версию приложения и присоединяйтесь к тестированию! Если у вас уже установлено мобильное приложение Яндекса, удалять его не нужно: бета-версия устанавливается отдельно и не мешает работе основного приложения. Мобильный Яндекс поможет решить ваши повседневные задачи. В нём есть сводка главных новостей дня, данные о погоде и ситуации на дорогах, быстрый поиск и многое другое. Установите виджет приложения и будьте в курсе событий дня. Голосовой помощник. Алиса умеет решать повседневные задачи: подскажет погоду и пробки по маршруту, посоветует, где поесть или купить продуктов, поставит будильник или напоминание на нужное время, найдёт что угодно в интернете. Алиса умеет не просто озвучивать информацию, но и рассказывать истории и поддержать разговор на любую тему - она постоянно обучается с помощью нейронной сети. Чтобы установить Алису основным Ассистентом, зайдите в меню Настройки своего смартфона, нажмите «Помощник и голосовой ввод» и выберите Яндекс. Автоматический определитель номера. Включите АОН в меню настроек и он покажет, кто звонит, даже если номера нет в контактах. База данных из более 5 миллионов организаций и отзывы пользователей сэкономят время и защитят от нежелательных разговоров. Доступен для смартфонов на базе Android 6.0 и выше. Внимание! Бета-версия – площадка для тестирования новых возможностей приложения. Она предназначена для опытных пользователей, готовых сообщать об ошибках и проблемах. Отправляйте ваши отзывы прямо через меню приложения или на почту: support@mobyandex.yandex.ru. Вместе мы сделаем приложение ещё лучше!

title: YouTube VR
description:
Näe kaikki YouTube-kanavat, ‑videot ja ‑sisällöntuottajat virtuaalitodellisuudessa.

YouTube VR ‑sovellus vie kaikki YouTube-videot uudistettuun virtuaalitodellisuuteen ja avaa ovet 3D-maailmaan, jota voi tarkastella sisältä päin. Saatavilla ensin Daydream View'ssä.

Koe YouTube aivan uudella tavalla.
 • Astu YouTuben sisään ja tutki sivustoa 3D VR ‑ympäristössä.
 • Katso ja tarkastele mitä tahansa YouTube-videota 360 asteen 3D-videoista tavallisiin videoihin.
 • Kirjautuneena voit tarkastella tilauksiasi, soittolistojasi, katseluhistoriaasi ja paljon muuta.

Näe ja kuule kaikki upea sisältö.
 • Uppoudu keskelle 360 asteen videoiden toimintaa.
 • Katso mitä tahansa tavallista videota virtuaalisella valkokankaalla erityisessä teatteritilassa.
 • Tilaäänen syvyys ja etäisyys riippuu siitä, mihin suuntaan katsot.

Tarkastele, selaa ja nauti kokemuksesta.
 • Videot näytetään ruudun keskellä, joten toisto on sujuvaa.
 • Voit käyttää sekä puheohjausta että näppäimiä ja selata ja etsiä sisältöä helposti.
 • Voit jopa selata uutta sisältöä videon toiston aikana.

Käyttöoikeusilmoitus
 • Mikrofoni tarvitaan YouTube-sisällön hakemiseksi puheohjauksella.

title: AncestryDNA - Genetic Testing
description:
Download the FREE AncestryDNA® app today and access the #1 selling consumer DNA test (DNA Kit purchase required). Start the journey to learn about your family story using some of the most advanced DNA science available.

Discover the unique family story that only your DNA can tell with a genetic test from AncestryDNA® , the world’s largest consumer DNA database.
With a simple test, you’ll get meaningful insights into who you are and where you came from and find new relatives who share your DNA.
With the AncestryDNA®  app you’ll get:
• Detailed Ethnic Origins -  AncestryDNA® doesn't just tell you which countries you're from, but can also pinpoint the specific places within them, giving you insightful geographic detail about your history with over 500 unique reports.
• Communities - Go deeper into your story with more specific details that connect you to the people, places, and migration paths in your family history, all from your DNA.
• Family Connections - You could discover a 3rd cousin for the first time by finding living relatives who share parts of your DNA.
• Easy to get started - Once you have purchased and received your DNA kit, simply take a photo of the barcode in your kit, follow a few quick instructions to activate and you’re done.
• Simple sharing - Show off your AncestryDNA®  results anytime, anywhere, including on your social networks.
• Notifications - You’ll always know what’s happening during your DNA test with status updates.
• Purchases -  Buy an AncestryDNA® test for yourself or gift a test to family or friends.

title: Package Tracker - Amazon, eBay, USPS, UPS, Wish
descriptionHTML:
Package tracking has never been so hassle-free and convenient as it becomes with Pkge.net. You can now conduct all mail tracking operations from one free app.

All the most current information on your domestic and international packages and parcels is available. Track your shipments with the help of the post office tracking number; perform a quick postal tracking lookup to check the location of your shipments; check the statuses of your packages – all the data is one click away in a simple, intuitive track app Pkge.net.

We offer a great solution saving time and nerves as you are expecting your air mail, parcel, or paquete to arrive. Now you’re protected from any emergencies or crises during the shipment due to the real-time postal service tracking service of Pkge.net.

This reliable parcel tracker provides a unique opportunity for users to perform international package tracking for multiple shipments even when they are still overseas. If your shipment was handled by one postal carrier at first and was later transferred to another carrier, the Pkge.net system will easily locate the shipment to inform you about its status and location. The only information you need for efficient and precise international tracking is the individual tracking number of your shipment. As soon as you find the track order number from your merchant and save it in the Pkge.net system, you’ll be receiving timely updates on the shipment’s status as it’s heading to your doorstep.

Pkge.net is the best package tracker currently available on the market and offering the following benefits to its users:
- Fast and efficient shipment tracking (including international tracking) by the parcel’s unique identifier;
- A unique system of international shipping tracking numbers’ identification for various countries and transit carriers;
- An ability to perform international parcel tracking in transit by various carriers;
- An opportunity to save several tracking numbers and receive updates on each of the shipment’s statuses in a real-time mode;
- No bothering built-in ads; no redundancy; only critical, hard-core functions and options;
- Minimum input from the user – all you need to provide is the individual tracking numbers;
- Online notifications about the shipment’s status changes.

Now you don’t need to register with each separate carrier handling your shipments from e-stores from all around the world. The tracking service of Pkge.net keeps all information in one place, so you can access the latest information on each parcel in one app, no matter where each of your packages is at the moment.

The free app version allows:
- Tracking of up to 15 shipments at the same time;
- Manual checking of the shipments’ statuses (automatic updates are available in the Premium version only);
- Delivery forecasting.

Pkge.net is a comprehensive luggage tracker with the help of which you’ll make the process of tracking parcels from 600+ postal carriers around the globe easy and convenient.
The system covers such popular carriers, as USPS, UPS, FedEx, Royal Mail, DHL Express, TNT, DPD, Hermes, Speedpak, China post, Ontrac, Lasership, Canada post, GLS, Eanwen, La Poste, Yun express, India post, Aramex, Yodel, Yunexpress, Japan Post, Australia Post, Deutsche Post, 4px, Colissimo, Hong Kong post, Singapore post, Chronopost, PostNL, Cainiao, Saudi post, Emirates post, and from online shops such as the Amazon, eBay, AliExpress, Wish, ASOS, Walmart, Etsy, Banggood, Gearbest, Allegro, Joom, Pandao, etc. We’re constantly expanding the list of partners to ensure universal global coverage and enable the clients to never lose their shipments out of sight at any stage of the transportation process.

No need to spend your time and effort on international mail tracking and global package tracking – Pkge.net can easily perform all these tasks for you in an instant. Do the shopping hassle-free; our app will keep you updated about each shipment that’s on its way to you.

title: Slice: Order delicious pizza from local pizzerias!
description:
From pepperoni to deep dish, find all the most delicious pizza at local restaurants in one place: Slice, the pizza app

With over 12,000 mom and pop pizza shops and counting, we give pizza lovers like you an amazing selection of local pizzerias. Not only do you get delicious food for pickup or delivery, you support small businesses and nearby pizzerias in your community.

Build your own delicious pizza.

You’re not picky, you just like your food how you like it. That’s why we made it easier to customize pizzas and other dishes, like mozzarella sticks and salads. Now you can add, say, mushrooms to one side of a pizza and extra cheese to another without searching the menu or leaving special instructions. 
 
Small mom and pops save, and so do pizza lovers.

Unlike other apps, we don’t charge local pizzerias insane commission and fees. They save with us, then pass it right back to you with exclusive pizza deals. Get them by turning on push notifications for promos and looking at the “Deals” section on every menu. Better yet, some shops surprise you with automatic savings at checkout. 

Reorder for pickup or delivery with one tap.

Found a pizza (or deal) you LOVE? Don’t search or build it again. Simple check your latest pizza orders and reorder in a tap. 

Hungry yet? We don’t blame you. Download Slice to order from a local pizzeria or restaurant. Remember: you can pick up food or have it delivered to your door. 

When you do, rate and review us below. It helps pizzerias and foodie near you. Happy eating!

title: Chase Mobile Checkout
description:
Accept credit cards for your business with your smartphone or tablet.

With a merchant services account and card reader from Chase and a smartphone or tablet, use Chase Mobile Checkout to accept payments on-the-go, virtually anywhere in the U.S., at any time.

Extend Your Business
• Be ready to take your customers’ payments when and where they are located.
• Take your business with you. Be able to process payments when you are away from your business, computer or credit card terminal.
• Allow additional employees to accept credit card payments on their smartphone or tablet.

Streamline Your Business
• Create a product catalog for easy checkout.
• Live, U.S. based, 24/7 telephone customer support.
• Have one payment processing relationship: Single statement, centralized reporting and one number to call for any issues. 
• Customize your employees’ access.  

Make It Easy For Your Customers
• Conduct faster transactions. If your customers are waiting in line, add an additional payment acceptance terminal with your smartphone or tablet.
• Bring the transaction to your customer. Allow your customers to pay anywhere in your store. Allow customers to pay for deliveries at the time of receipt.
• Send customers’ electronic receipts via email or text. 

Help Protect Your Customers and Your Business
• Credit card information is encrypted at the time of the card swipe or insertion and during transmission and processing.
• Geo-location features allow you to determine the location of the transaction, which helps with dispute settlement. Location map is printed on receipt.

Take Your Business With You
• Easier reconciliation. View information about your Chase merchant services account from your smartphone or tablet.
• Search for individual transactions and review account activity.
• Process refunds and voids.

To process transactions, you must have a merchant services account with Chase, install the Chase Mobile Checkout app on your mobile device and use a mobile card reader from Chase. In order to pair your mobile device with the reader, it must meet minimum requirements of Android 6.0 and Bluetooth® 4.0. Businesses are required to complete an application and agree to terms and conditions at the time of enrollment. All businesses are subject to credit approval.  Merchant services are provided by Paymentech, LLC (“Chase”), a subsidiary of JPMorgan Chase Bank, N.A.

There is no charge to download this app, but depending on your merchant service account terms, there may be charges associated with the purchase and shipment of the card reader. When using the app, message and data rates may apply. Such charges include, but are not limited to, those from your communications service provider. In addition, all applicable processing fees outlined in the merchant services contract with Chase will be assessed for all transactions initiated through the app.

Transaction processing may be interrupted for various reasons, including service outages affecting your smartphone or tablet, wireless or Internet provider, technology failures, and system capacity limitations.

Android is a registered trademark of Google Inc.

title: VR Flight: Airplane Pilot Simulator (Cardboard)
description: Virtual Reality (VR) Flight gives you the real feeling of flying an airplane. Ready to be a professional pilot? Jump into the world of VR Flight and take to the skies as you fly your plane above a dense populated city environment. Although many forms of non-motorized aerosports like skydiving, hang gliding or a even wingsuit diving can bring exhilarating thrills, the feeling of controlling a large piece of flying metal in the skies is something that gives tremendous empowerment. The combination of virtual reality, pixel perfect graphics and a realistic (yet easy) flight sim model gives you this true sensation. Are you the next hero in the skies? Controls The controls are easy and intuitive and work on phones with or without a gyroscope. To turn left/right tilt your head in that direction. You'll feel the plane bank accordingly. To dive down tilt your head downwards and you'll start dropping altitude and flying towards the ground. To climb tilt upward and you'll start gaining altitude. Take some time to practice and you'll soon master the skies like a true pro. Sit back and enjoy the view - Passenger (demo) flight Just want to relax and enjoy the experience and view? No worries you can select Passenger Flight from the main menu and a professional pilot will tour you around the city and you can relax and view the sites in gorgeous 360 VR. Large Map The city environment beneath you is crafted in great details with awesome special effects such as the blue reflection of the skyscraper windows. The light red haze in the distance as the morning breaks and the morning fog all make the city feel realistic. The flying area is a huge (infinite) flight map allowing you to freely roam the skies without flight plan. Choose your flight path, but always be aware of your surroundings and be aware of you flight controls and horizon. In free flight mode you can to what you want, how you want. Prefer an air race type flying style with aerobatic flight maneuvers, or do you like gently gliding the skies like an angel? This sim lets you experience real flight. Overcome your fear Do you have fear of flying? Take the bull by the horns and start flying a plane now. This is a gentle way to experience flight and overcome your fear of flying. Send your ideas Please leave a review with any comments or ideas; we're planning great updates featuring new planes, locations and missions. We look forward to hear from you and who knows, maybe your suggestions will be in the next update. ________________________________ Find more on your VR Discovery and join us on social media: - Like us on Facebook - View our videos on YouTube - Follow us on Twitter
descriptionHTML:
Virtual Reality (VR) Flight gives you the real feeling of flying an airplane.

Ready to be a professional pilot? Jump into the world of VR Flight and take to the skies as you fly your plane above a dense populated city environment.

Although many forms of non-motorized aerosports like skydiving, hang gliding or a even wingsuit diving can bring exhilarating thrills, the feeling of controlling a large piece of flying metal in the skies is something that gives tremendous empowerment. The combination of virtual reality, pixel perfect graphics and a realistic (yet easy) flight sim model gives you this true sensation. Are you the next hero in the skies?

Controls
The controls are easy and intuitive and work on phones with or without a gyroscope. To turn left/right tilt your head in that direction. You'll feel the plane bank accordingly.

To dive down tilt your head downwards and you'll start dropping altitude and flying towards the ground. To climb tilt upward and you'll start gaining altitude.

Take some time to practice and you'll soon master the skies like a true pro.

Sit back and enjoy the view - Passenger (demo) flight
Just want to relax and enjoy the experience and view? No worries you can select Passenger Flight from the main menu and a professional pilot will tour you around the city and you can relax and view the sites in gorgeous 360 VR.

Large Map
The city environment beneath you is crafted in great details with awesome special effects such as the blue reflection of the skyscraper windows. The light red haze in the distance as the morning breaks and the morning fog all make the city feel realistic. The flying area is a huge (infinite) flight map allowing you to freely roam the skies without flight plan. Choose your flight path, but always be aware of your surroundings and be aware of you flight controls and horizon. In free flight mode you can to what you want, how you want. Prefer an air race type flying style with aerobatic flight maneuvers, or do you like gently gliding the skies like an angel? This sim lets you experience real flight.

Overcome your fear
Do you have fear of flying? Take the bull by the horns and start flying a plane now. This is a gentle way to experience flight and overcome your fear of flying.

Send your ideas
Please leave a review with any comments or ideas; we're planning great updates featuring new planes, locations and missions. We look forward to hear from you and who knows, maybe your suggestions will be in the next update.

title: Mobilbank DK – Danske Bank
description:
Mobilbanken giver dig overblik og frihed til at ordne økonomien uafhængigt af tid og sted. Den gør det nemt at være i dialog med os og tage beslutninger i både små og store økonomiske spørgsmål.


Du kan blandt andet:
- Betale regninger og overføre penge – uden NemID
- Bestille lommepenge-app og andre produkter til børn og unge
- Underskrive aftaler digitalt
- Booke møde online
- Få adgang til dine betalingskonti i andre banker
- Opdatere dine person- og kontaktoplysninger
- Tilpasse kontooversigten efter dit eget behov.


Udviklingen stopper ikke her – vi opdaterer jævnligt appen med nye og spændende muligheder.

 

Nemt at komme i gang

1. Hent appen
2. Log på med dit CPR-nr. og din servicekode til mobilbank
3. Så er du i gang.
 

Har du glemt din servicekode, finder du den i netbanken under ”Mobile tjenester”.

 
Har du ikke mobilbank i forvejen, så tilmelder du dig i netbanken under ”Mobile tjenester”.

 
God fornøjelse

title: Ilmatieteen laitoksen sää
description:
Paistaako Naantalissa tunnin päästä aurinko? Sataako Singaporessa ensi viikolla? Liukastellaanko Lohjalla? 

Ilmatieteen laitoksen sääpalvelusta näet jopa 10 vuorokauden sääennusteen yli 17 000 paikkaan Suomessa sekä tuhansiin ulkomaiden kohteisiin. Jos puhelimesi paikannustoiminto on päällä, palvelu näyttää automaattisesti sijaintisi säätiedot. Voit tallentaa palveluun suosikkipaikkakuntasi, ja voit näppärästi selata paikkakuntien sää- ja havaintotietoja. Nyt voit tarkistaa myös säähän liittyvät varoitukset Suomessa. Sataako tunnin päästä? Voit helposti tarkistaa palvelusta sateen todennäköisyysprosentin sekä ennustetun sademäärän. Nyt voit myös ilmoittaa omat säähavaintosi meille.

SÄÄ-palvelun ominaisuuksia: 

-sääennusteet yli 17 000 paikkakunnalle Suomessa ja suurimmat ulkomaiden kohteet, 
-10 vuorokauden sääennusteet, 
-sääennuste tunnin tarkkuudella seuraavan 48 tunnin ajaksi, 
-7 kertaa vuorokaudessa päivittyvät varoitukset Suomessa, 
-paikkakuntakohtaiset varoitukset Suomessa, 
-säähavainnot Suomessa ja ulkomailla, 
-sateen todennäköisyys, 
-sateen määrä, 
-tuulen suunta ja nopeus, 
-auringon nousu ja laskuaika, 
-tuntuu kuin -lämpötila, 
-ei mainoksia.

title: PARGI.EE
description:
PARGI.EE on Telia poolt ametlikult toetatud m-parkimise rakendus, mida saavad kasutada Telia, Elisa ja Tele2 kliendid. See on kõige värskema parkimistsoonide andmebaasiga lahendus Eestis. Uute tsoonide lisandumisel või tingimuste muutumisel uuendatakse sisu automaatselt (rakendust ei ole vaja uuendada). Rakendus kuvab lähimaid parkimistsoone, võimaldab lisada kuni 5 auto numbrit, kuvab detailset parkimisajalugu koos maksumustega kuni 6 kuud tagasi, tuletab meelde aktiivsest parkimisest, lubab seada limiite, teavitab limiidi täitumisest ja võimaldab limiiti pikendada. Ülevaate oma kõikidest m-parkimistest pikema aja jooksul saab veebilehelt www.pargi.ee (parkimine).

PARGI.EE rakendus töötab üle andmeside ühenduse, kuid osa funktsionaalsusest on dubleeritud SMS'i ja kõnega.

title: Iltalehti
description:
Suositun Iltalehti-sovelluksen avulla seuraat luetuimpia ja tuoreimpia uutisia helposti ja nopeasti. Lataa nyt, niin tiedät, mistä muut puhuvat!

Sovelluksesta löydät aina:
- Kaikki tuoreimmat uutiset sekä Suomesta että maailmalta
- Tärkeimmät ja puhutuimmat tapahtumat niin urheilukentiltä kuin viihdemaailmastakin
- Vinkkejä ja kiinnostavia tarinoita elämän kaikilta osa-alueilta Lifestyle-osastoilta
- IL-TV:n monipuolisen videotarjonnan Sensuroimaton Päivärinta -keskusteluohjelmasta Bundesliiga-matseihin ja kotimaan ykkösuutisista kansainvälisiin somehitteihin
- Tuoreimmat säätiedot omasta sijainnistasi
- Fingerporin, horoskoopin, ristikot ja sudokut sekä vaikka mitä muuta ajanvietesisältöä

- Osastoja ja artikkeleita voit selata pyyhkäisemällä

title: Mobil-ID
description:
Mobil-ID er en app fra Danske Bank som du laster ned på din mobiltelefon og som lager engangskoder til bruk i nett-, brett- og mobilbanken.

 

Mobil-ID tar du i bruk ved å:

• laste ned appen på din telefon

• bestille tjenesten «Mobil-ID» fra nettbanken eller ved å ringe kundesenteret på telefon 987 08540

• aktivere appen på din telefon

 

Som den del av aktiveringen av Mobil-ID på din telefon vil du motta en aktiveringskode på SMS. Denne koden benyttes kun ved aktiveringen og ikke når du tar Mobil-ID i bruk.

 

Du finner mer informasjon om Mobil-ID på vår hjemmeside danskebank.no/mobilid

title: Nordea Mobile - Sverige
description:
Med hjälp av appen sköter du enkelt dagliga bankärenden. 
Den nya mobilbanksversionen innehåller en uppdaterad översikt över dina finanser och andra nya funktioner. 

Prova hur smidigt den är! 
1. Ladda ned appen genom att klicka på Ladda ned.
2. Logga in med BankID. Färdigt! 

Med appen Nordea Mobile kan du sköta de flesta dagliga bankärendena och den är alltid nära till hands.

Exempel på appens funktioner:
•	Du får en snabb översikt över din ekonomi.
•	Du betalar snabbt och enkelt.
•	Med hjälp av appen kan du kontakta Nordea via chatt, telefon eller e-post.
•	Du ser alla dina besparingar och placeringar på samma ställe.
	
Tips: - Aktivera fingeravtrycksidentifieringen i inställningarna så kan du logga in på Nordea Mobile direkt med ditt fingeravtryck.

- Du kan anpassa din startsida genom att klicka på pennan uppe i högra hörnet. Här kan du lägga till, ta bort och ändra placeringen av apparna på startsidan. 
   
Vill du veta mer om fördelarna med mobilbanken eller behöver du hjälp? Vi betjänar på numret 0771-22 44 88

title: Payanywhere Credit Card Reader & Point of Sale POS
description: The Payanywhere Point of Sale (POS) app, credit card readers, and Smart Solution Suite are the business payment solutions you need to transform your business’s payments. Manage all your customer’s payments with the Payanywhere point of sale payment app. From farmers markets to coffee shops to mom & pop shops, the Payanywhere POS app has got you and your customers covered! Easily accept debit and credit card payments with our mobile credit card readers, manage your inventory, send invoices, and generate receipts - all through our free POS mobile app for Android. With Payanywhere’s point of sale (POS) app and compatible card readers, your customers can swipe, insert, or tap their cards – no matter where you are! Payanywhere’s credit card readers are even compatible with mobile payments like Android Pay, Samsung Pay, and Apple Pay. The Payanywhere POS Android app and free online portal has everything you need to run your business successfully. Our Point of Sale (POS) solution makes accepting payments simple. Cash, credit cards, and contactless payments are all supported to help you serve your customers. Streamline your day-to-day operations and easily keep track of inventory, manage invoicing, view transaction reporting, and order additional credit card readers from wherever you do business. Why Payanywhere’s Point of Sale (POS) app and compatible card readers? - Credit card reader solutions for mobile payments or point of sale (POS) hardware. Accept chip card, magstripe, and NFC contactless payments. - Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover, and AliPay — accepted all at competitive rates. Manage invoicing — send invoices from the Payanywhere point of sale (POS) app. Allow your customers to set up autopay. - Let customers easily pay with Android Pay, Samsung Pay, and Apple Pay with their mobile devices. - Easily split payments, accept tips, and allow customers to sign for their transactions from your mobile point of sale (POS) system. - Email, text, and print receipts. - Create open tickets and tabs for food and drink orders. - Keep track of stock with inventory management tools. EASY ONLINE SIGN UP Signing up for your business payment solution is easier than ever with Payanywhere’s online application. Get started today by creating an account in the app or at shop.payanywhere.com. 1. Sign up online or in the app. 2. Pick the pay as you go plan or contact us for custom pricing. 3. Select your hardware. ---------- Phone Swipe users: Continue to accept credit cards by uninstalling Phone Swipe and downloading the Payanywhere app. The mobile POS card reader features and functionality are the same as Phone Swipe, and all of your app settings and information will transfer over. Log in to Payanywhere using the same login credentials. To learn more about Payanywhere and mobile Point of Sale solutions, visit payanywhere.com. Contact salesreps@payanywhere.com for custom pricing. Please email any comments or suggestions to feedback@payanywhere.com.

title: Idle Port Tycoon - Sea port empire
description:
The sea is a harsh mistress, become its master and save the world in Idle Port Tycoon game!

Aye! Aye! Captain! That’s right. The fate of the world is in your hands in this ship game. 

With an alien attack on the horizon and earth set to fall, there’s no time for fun, games and sea shanties. It’s up to you and your team to travel to the past and build the defenses in the seaport.

Can you become a successful seaport tycoon in time to thwart their mission?

The challenge is tough, but, in this ship game, your plan is simple:

1. Build a port, unload cargo and earn idle money
2. Advance your port empire with more and more sea ports
3. Build defenses along the coasts and SAVE THE WORLD!


All you need to do is use your tapping skill and build, build, build. Tap the ship game screen to add containers & cargo, load them up, transfer those cargoes, upgrade, and win!

Keep counting that coin as ships doc in your harbor, bringing you even more shipping containers. Tap to increase your specs, gain more materials, build your empire and level up to the max in this ship game!

With the fate of the world hanging in the balance. Are you ready to become a sea port tycoon in Idle Port Tycoon?

Download it now to find out!

title: Telia HSEQ
description:
Dette er Telia AS' app til bruk ved innrapportering av HMS-hendelser og kvalitetsrelaterte saker. Appen inneholder systematikk for å sende melding om avvik, observasjoner, nestenulykker, ulykker og forbedringsforslag, samt en egen modul for dokumentasjon av gjennomførte sikker-jobb analyser / risikoanalyser og en annen for inspeksjoner og revisjoner. 

Appen er strippet for alle unødvendige funksjoner og knapper for å gjøre den mest mulig brukervennlig. Likevel er det et komplett rapporteringsverktøy som oppfyller alle våre krav og behov, og vi anser forbedringsmulighetene ved å bruke appen i bedriften vår for store. 

Vi i Telia tror på KIS-prinsippet. Keep It Simple. Alt for mange organisasjoner lager HMSK-systemene sine for kompliserte, noe som resulterer i underrapportering og en mengde byråkratisk rot. 

Vår app, som er en skreddersøm av den originale «HSEQ Free» fra Mellora AS, skal skape HMSK-entusiasme! 

Appen er koblet til www.hseqreports.com for oppfølging og behandling av alle saker. Du vil trenge brukernavn og passord for å kunne bruke appen til rapportering.

title: Dernières Nouvelles d'Alsace
description:
Découvrez la toute nouvelle version de l’application des DNA. Entièrement repensée, elle est plus confortable, plus rapide et plus simple à utiliser. Avec les toutes nouvelles Unes Locales, il vous est proposé de choisir une page d’accueil proche de vous, qui intègre les informations qui vous concernent le plus directement ; vous pouvez aussi composer dans « Mes actus » une page personnelle qui reprend les rubriques qui vous intéressent particulièrement. Gardez ainsi le lien en temps réel avec toute l’actu de votre région.

L'application des DNA c'est l'information des principales villes de la région Alsace de Strasbourg à Mulhouse en passant par Colmar, Haguenau, Wissembourg, Saverne, Sarre-Union, Obernai, Molsheim, Sélestat, Guebwiller, Saint-Louis, Altkirch … , sans oublier les 883 communes couvertes par les journalistes des  Dernières Nouvelles d’Alsace.

Retrouvez les infos essentielles du moment sélectionnées par la rédaction des DNA : 
● Toute l’actualité en direct, minute par minute, pour ne pas manquer d’infos importantes.

title: Yle Lasten Areena
description:
Lasten Areenassa voi helposti ja turvallisesti katsella ja kuunnella Ylen lastenohjelmia!

Sovelluksesta löytyy lastenohjelmia jaoteltuna iän ja kielen mukaan. Pikku Kakkonen tarjoaa ohjelmia perheen pienemmille, ja Galaxi on koululaisten oma tv. BUU-klubben tarjoaa ruotsinkielistä lastenohjelmaa pienemmille ja Hajbo kouluikäisille.

Sovellukseen julkaistaan uutta sisältöä päivittäin. Sovelluksesta löytyy myös paljon kuunneltavia lastensisältöjä, kuten satuja, kuunnelmia ja musiikkia vaikkapa automatkalle.

Uudistunut sovellus muistaa katsotut ohjelmat ja jatkaa automaattisesti kesken jääneestä kohdasta. Sarjan jaksot toistuvat automaattisesti peräkkäin, mutta voit halutessasi muuttaa toimintoa asetuksista. Sovellus tukee nyt myös Chromecastia, jolla voit toistaa ohjelmat tv:ssä.

Sovellusta voi käyttää suomen- tai ruotsinkielisenä. Voit myös valita ohjelmille tekstityksen.

Sovellus toimii puhelimilla ja tableteilla ja vaatii vähintään Android 4.1 käyttöjärjestelmän. 

Osa ohjelmista on tekijänoikeussyistä rajattu vain Suomessa katseltavaksi.

Lähetä palautteesi ja kehitysehdotukset sähköpostiin.

title: NetSupport DNA Console
description:
This app is provided as a supporting tool for NetSupport DNA, a complete IT Asset Management solution, delivering a suite of features to help support the management and maintenance of IT assets across any company or school enterprise.

The DNA mobile app allows a Technician, when away from their desk, to search for and view a detailed Hardware and Software Inventory for any PC on the network. 

The mobile app also includes a QR code scanner to help instantly identify any PC, either from an on-screen QR code displayed by DNA, or from a label fixed to the device. NetSupport DNA also provides a QR code label creation facility, including support for custom details. Histories of all hardware changes as well as any software installs or removals are also shown on the app.

In addition to the Inventory and History views, the NetSupport DNA mobile app also highlights any new PC alerts that have triggered across the network. 

If you’re new to NetSupport DNA, learn more at www.netsupportdna.com and download the required Server, desktop Console and Agent (Client) components needed to complete your installation.

Note: To connect this app to your NetSupport DNA installation you need to download the DNA Web Server from our website. 

If you wish to test this application, you may use this test server:

Address: mobile.netsupportdna.com 
Username: Admin
Password: dna

title: Abandoned World - Urbex
description:
Abandoned World *officially* allows you to discover the exact location of Urbex spots. Easy to use and functional! Exploration is guaranteed!

>> Finally a different type of exploration around you. Stop following the mainstream & go off the beaten track.

-- WHY YOU’LL LOVE ABANDONED WORLD

 * FREE. No Ads
 * Interactive & modern design
 * Accurate location
 * Upload your own pictures
 * Upload your own abandoned spot
 * Navigation support (with Google Maps navigation)
 * Save your favorites places

Our goal is to provide location and picture to urban past and abandoned or forgotten places. Commonly named Urbex.

Enjoy learning historical facts or simply refresh their own memories and opinions as they share. We strive to publish simple content that adds a twinkle of nostalgia and a spark of insight to our lives.

The purpose of this type of tourism is to visit abandoned places, get appreciative pleasure, many of these researchers are photographers.

Thank you for trying out this FREE app get ready to feel great emotions.

-- WE LOVE FEEDBACK --
As always, we appreciate your feedback.
Please keep sharing your experience to contact@itsabandoned.com
Do you love our app? Please rate and review us in the store!

-- START EXPLORING --

title: NemID nøgleapp
description:
NemID nøgleapp er et supplement til det eksisterende NemID nøglekort, og med denne officielle app får du NemID direkte på din smartphone og tablet.

Appen giver dig adgang til bla. netbank, borger.dk, sundhed.dk og private aktørers hjemmesider som f.eks. fagforening eller a-kasse.

Appen fungerer med en firecifret kode eller fingeraftryksgenkendelse.

Af sikkerhedsmæssige årsager, kan NemID nøgleapp ikke køre på telefoner og tablets der er rooted.

Bankerne og den offentlige sektor står bag NemID nøgleapp.

Appen er udviklet af e-nettet A/S. Nets A/S er leverandør af infrastrukturen.
For support se mere på: www.nemid.nu

title: Shopfully - Weekly Ads & Deals
description: On Shopfully, you’ll find deals at Walmart, Target, Kmart, Dollar Tree, Bed Bath &Beyond, Big Lots, RadioShack, Staples, Coldwater Creek and many other big-name stores! Shopfully International Group is a leading digital platform used by over 30 million users worldwide when getting ready to go shopping in their neighborhood. The platform contains a variety of information including details about promotions, new products, shops, opening times and contacts of the main retailers and brands in each shopping category, geolocated in one place and easily accessible to users. Shopfully is eco-friendly: it helps save trees by transforming paper ads to digital format, making it easy to flip through them when you want and where you want using your smartphone, tablet or computer without harming the environment. Don't miss out on the best offers, with Shopfully you can save them and organize your shopping. Consult your saved offers in any moment in the Memo section and always know when they are about to expire. An alert will notify you when the promotions are about to end. Main features of app: ✔WEEKLY ADS: quickly search and browse all the weekly ads in your neighborhood ✔ DEALS: discover the best deals of the week selected by our staff ✔ MAP: use the built-in map to find the location of any store including address and phone number, then choose your preferred navigation program to get directions with one click ✔ STORE HOURS: decide where to do your shopping on Sundays and holidays thanks to always up-to-date store hours ✔ ALERTS: get notified of the latest sales and price cuts at the stores where you shop ✔ FAVORITES: save your favorite ads and deals so you can easily access them while shopping To send us feedback or ask a question, write to info@shopfully.com You’ll find big name retailers such as Walmart, Target, Kmart, Sears, Best Buy, Staples, Home Depot, Bed Bath & Beyond and many others. Never miss a sale! Saving money with paperless weekly ads and catalogs is a breeze with Shopfully, making it easy to find the best deals and promotions when you shop! Save your favorite ads and catalogs with the tap of a finger and flip through them whenever you want!

title: Coupons.com – Grocery Coupons & Cash Back Savings
description:
Save $100s with free grocery coupons and deals at your favorite stores like Walmart, Target, Kroger and Dollar General. You’ll have access to hundreds of coupons on the brands you love, making saving money effortless. Best of all, you can manage all your grocery shopping and coupons right from your phone, in one single app, without ever relying on a printer or shuffling between multiple store apps.

Join the millions of shoppers who use the Coupons.com app to shop and save easily at your favorite grocery stores. Enjoy two ways to save: One, simply link your store loyalty cards to your Coupons.com account, then add coupons with a tap to save seamlessly at the register. The dollars fall off at purchase.

Two, if your store doesn’t have a loyalty card, get cash back after purchase. Just choose the coupons you like and add them to the stores you want to redeem them at–all in the app– then submit a picture of your receipt after purchase. After your purchase is verified, you’ll get cash back in your PapPal account. So easy! 

No printing, no paper, no hassle—it’s a cinch now to save on food, baby and toddler items, pet food, medicine and personal care. We have coupons from all your favorite brands like Tide, Bounty, Cheerios, Kraft, Kellogg’s, General Mills, Campbell’s, Dole, Betty Crocker, M&M’s, Perdue, Crest, Pantene and more.

Here’s how it works:

1) After you download the free app, sign in to your Coupons.com account (or sign up if you’re new—it’s quick and easy).

2) Link your store loyalty cards to your Coupons.com account.  If your store doesn’t have a loyalty card, you can still save by using cash back grocery coupons—we’ll tell you how in a second.

3) Next, browse through 100s of free grocery coupons by store and add them with just a tap.

4) Load up your cart at the store and follow your shopping list in the app to make sure you’re using all the grocery coupons you’ve chosen. 

5) Then save one of two ways: Instantly at checkout or after your purchase. Stores with loyalty cards give you instant savings, while other stores require a quick picture of your receipt. Simply send us the photo, we’ll verify your purchase, then put cash into your PayPal account as soon as possible. The best part: You won’t have to wait to reach a minimum amount in order to get your money.

What you’ll love:

• Easily save $100s on your favorite brands with offers that are added daily. Plus, watch for Coupons.com-exclusive offers that you can redeem for free items, like bananas, coffee, or potatoes.

• Tap-and-save simplicity with 100s of verified digital grocery, drug and discount store coupons from your favorite brands that you can use on your mobile device.

• Add all your store loyalty cards to just one app! No need to juggle several cards or accounts. Once you link them to your Coupons.com app, all your grocery coupons will be in one spot, making grocery planning, shopping, and saving easier than ever.

• No loyalty card at your store? No problem. Get cash back after purchase by simply adding coupons, making your purchase, then sending us a photo of your receipt after checkout. The best part: There’s no minimum purchase required to get cash back! 

• Put away your scissors and never worry about forgetting your coupons. All your grocery savings will be digital, making the shopping and saving process easier and more organized for you.  However, don’t fret: If you still prefer to print your coupons, you can do so directly from the app.

If you’re looking for grocery savings at stores like Target, Walmart, Albertsons, Safeway, Winn-Dixe, Meijer, Food Lion and more, the Coupons.com app is the one-stop shop for all your grocery coupons, deals and savings.

Awards Won:
Appy, May 2017
Best Mobile App Awards, April 2017

We love our customers.
Having trouble with the app?
Contact our friendly support team and we'll get you back to saving in a snap: 
androidapp-support@coupons.com. 

Coupons.com is a Quotient brand.

title: Nordea Business DK
description:
Nordea Business Mobile er Nordeas nye app til erhvervskunder. Den nye app gør det muligt at håndtere virksomhedens daglige bankforretninger hvor som helst, når som helst. Du kan hurtigt få adgang og overblik over virksomhedens konti, ind- og udgående transaktioner samt mulighed for at lave betalinger, overføre penge og meget mere…

- Log på med Touch ID eller Face ID
- Se saldi på konti og oplysninger om transaktioner
- Se lån, kreditter og kommende betalinger
- Overfør penge til andre og mellem egne konti
- Opret og godkend en eller flere betalinger/regninger
- Godkend betalinger med bekræftelse fra to personer
- Skift aftale, hvis du har flere aftaler
- Start en chat med en af vores medarbejdere
- Book og deltag i onlinemøder med vores rådgivere
- Ryst telefonen for at logge af

For at kunne bruge Nordea Business kræves der en onlineaftale til Netbank Erhverv med NemID. Læs mere om Nordea Business Mobile på https://www.nordea.dk/erhverv/produkter/digitale-services/Nordea-Business.html

title: Visited Cities
description:
Do you want to keep a record of all the places you have visited? Visited Cities lets you pin the cities you have been to on a beautiful map! Most apps only allow you to mark entire countries or states, but with Visited Cities you can visualize exactly where you have been.

++ HUGE CITY DATABASE

Look up cities in a huge database which includes every city with over 10.000 inhabitants. You can also pin any place you want in the map by tapping there for two seconds. 

++ COMPLETE STATS

How many continents have you visited? Which percentage of countries in the whole world and in each continent? 

++ MAKE YOUR WISHLIST

Which cities do you want to visit next? Create your wishlist and plan your trips!

++ SHARE!

Share a beautiful image of you map on any social network. You can also share your stats.

++ BACK UP YOUR DATA

Log in to Facebook to back up your data, so you will neve loose it if you switch devices.

++ FIND YOUR FRIENDS

See your Facebook friends' maps and check which cities they have been to.

++ TEST YOU KNOWLEDGE

How much do you know about the cities you have visited? Find out with the quiz!

title: DNA Prepaid
description:
DNA Prepaid -sovelluksella voit hallinnoida DNA:n prepaid-liittymääsi sekä ostaa kätevästi aikapohjaisia nettiyhteyksiä 3 tunnista 30 päivään. Sovellus ilmoittaa, kun yhteys on loppumassa, ja tarjoaa jatkoa.
 
Sovellus auttaa mm. kulujen hallinnassa. Voit ostaa edullisia datapaketteja päiväkohtaisen dataveloituksen sijaan. Sovelluksen käyttö on DNA:n prepaid-liittymistä veloituksetonta.
 
 
Sovelluksen avulla voit esimerkiksi:
- tarkistaa liittymäsi saldon ja puhelinnumeron.
- tarkistaa liittymätyypin ja voimassaoloajan.
- tarkastella veloitushistoriaa.
- tarkastella käytössä ja jonossa olevia ostamiasi paketteja.
- asettaa turvanumeron, johon voit soittaa rajoitetusti vaikka liittymäsaldosi on lopussa.
- ladata puheaikaa ja saldoa.
- käyttää sovellusta suomeksi, ruotsiksi tai englanniksi ja samalla vaikuttaa myös liittymäsi kieleen.

title: T-Sky
description: Back up your photos and videos Keep your photos and videos safe with unlimited storage. All your photos will be stored in Norway. We keep your original image size and quality, of course. Scroll down memory lane Rediscover a lifetime of memories. You can easily scroll months and years back in time, right on your phone. It's super fast! Automatically organized Photos are organized by time and place. And you can create your own albums of photos for important events in your life. View all your photos See all your photos, not just the ones stored on your device. You can browse your entire photo library anywhere. Friendly sharing Create albums with your friends. Any one of your friends can contribute their own faves. Sharing is fun and private. Free up space on your phone Make room for new photos and videos on your phone. T-Sky can free up space by deleting local versions of your photos that have been backed up already. RAW We support a wide range of RAW formats, perfect for photo enthusiasts.
descriptionHTML:
Back up your photos and videos
Keep your photos and videos safe with unlimited storage. All your photos will be stored in Norway. We keep your original image size and quality, of course.

Scroll down memory lane
Rediscover a lifetime of memories. You can easily scroll months and years back in time, right on your phone. It's super fast!

Automatically organized
Photos are organized by time and place. And you can create your own albums of photos for important events in your life.

View all your photos
See all your photos, not just the ones stored on your device. You can browse your entire photo library anywhere.

Friendly sharing
Create albums with your friends. Any one of your friends can contribute their own faves. Sharing is fun and private.

Free up space on your phone
Make room for new photos and videos on your phone. T-Sky can free up space by deleting local versions of your photos that have been backed up already.

RAW
We support a wide range of RAW formats, perfect for photo enthusiasts.

title: PayPal Mobile Cash: Send and Request Money Fast
description:
Our new PayPal app is a simple and secure way to get paid back for last night’s takeaway, send money to friends who have an account with PayPal  , check PayPal activity, choose currencies to send around the world and more. Plus, we’ve added some new features we think you’ll love…

*NEW* A TOUCH-FREE WAY TO PAY OR BE PAID
•	If you’re buying, simply scan the QR code to pay securely with your PayPal app.
•	Whatever you’re selling, now you can quickly set up a QR code and get paid in person, all with just your phone. 

SEND AND REQUEST MONEY FOR FREE 
•	When funded by a bank account or balance, it’s free and secure to send money or ask for it back from friends and family in the US.
•	All you need is an email address, mobile number, bank account, cash pick up service point or mobile top up details. *An account with PayPal is required to send and receive money. If you don’t have an account with PayPal, you can sign up for free quickly and easily.
•	NEW FEATURE: just type a name, email or phone number and PayPal will find the right person for you. 
•	Request money quickly and securely from friends or family with just a few taps.

GET INSTANT SPENDING NOTIFICATIONS 
•	Never miss a thing – keep on top of payments and sending or receiving money, with instant push notifications.
•	Check out all your latest PayPal activity, by just logging in. 

ACCESS YOUR BALANCE INSTANTLY WITH THE PAYPAL CASH CARD
•	Easily transfer funds from your bank balance to your account with PayPal. 
•	Shop in-store, online or everywhere Mastercard® is accepted and withdraw cash at ATMs worldwide.  
•	PayPal Cash Plus account required to get the card.

TRUST PAYPAL SECURE TRANSACTIONS
•	You can be sure PayPal will help keep your financial information secure, with commercially available encryption, and fraud detection. All that plus monitoring transactions, 24/7.

Not all features may be available in your market.

title: Aktuelle Prospekte, Angebote & Rabatte Online
description:
Supermarkt Rabatt Broschüren - Aktuelle Prospekt und Angebote
Alle aktuelle Prospekte und Angeboten, Wöchentliche Prospekte , aktuellen broschüren, Alle Prospekte Online

Erhalten Sie Informationen über Supermarktrabatte😍

Mit dem aktuellen Produktkatalog können Sie die digitalen Kataloge der Supermärkte über eine einzige Anwendung verfolgen. Mit der aktuellen Produktkatalog-Anwendung können Sie täglich die aktuellsten Supermarktbroschüren, Supermarktrabatte und Supermarktkataloge einsehen.

Aktueller Produktkatalog; Diese App nutzt einen sehr geringen Datenfluss und verbraucht daher nicht Ihr mobiles Internetpaket. Wir möchten Ihnen die aktuellen Produktkataloge aller Supermärkte kostenlos anbieten, indem wir Ihnen mitteilen, welche sagenhaften Kampagnen es gibt.👌

Aktueller Rewe Produktkatalog; Hier können Sie täglich, wöchentlich oder monatliche Rewe Supermarktrabatt-Broschüren und Rewe Supermarkt-Kampagnen einsehen. Die Anwendung ist kostenlos und verbraucht nur sehr geringe Mengen Daten von Ihrem Internet-Paket.

Wir wollten eine kostenlose Plattform für Sie schaffen, auf der Sie wöchentlich aktuelle Zeitschriften, Broschüren und Kataloge der beliebtesten Supermärkte wie Rewe, Lidl, Aldi, Norma, Kaufland, famila, Real, Metro, Kodi, Edeka, Netto, Penny, Rossman, Barrique, bio  Markt, Bofrost, Feneberg, Getränkeland, Hit Markt, Krümet, Müller, Obi,  und und viele Märkte einsehen können.


Supermärkten und Discountern, wöchentlich oder monatlich zu den aktuellen Produktbroschüren ihrer Publikationen, Kataloge, Beilagen, können in Echtzeit von Ihrem Handy oder Tablet aus verfolgt werden.

Mit der Mobile-Anwendung Aktuelle Supermarktprodukte;

✅ können Sie alle Supermarktkampagnen in Kategorien wie wöchentlich und monatlich einsehen
✅nehmen die angezeigten Bilder nur sehr wenig Platz ein und Ihr Internetpaket wird dadurch nicht aufgebraucht
✅erhalten Sie, sobald aktuelle Produkte eintreffen, eine kostenlose Benachrichtigung
✅können Sie die Bilder vergrößern und dadurch die Produkte und Informationen detailliert betrachten
✅ können Sie das aktuelle Produkt, das Ihnen gefällt, mit Ihren Freunden oder auf Ihren sozialen Medien teilen
✅können Sie Ihre Einkaufsliste kostenlos erstellen
✅ können Sie sich mit Hilfe des Notizbuchs Notizen machen

Es wird Ihnen auf Ihrem Handy oder im laufenden Betrieb zur Verfügung stehen, sobald Sie Broschüren, Kataloge, Beilagen, einschließlich Markenprodukte, aktuelle Produkte von Geschäften oder Geschäften, mit dieser Anwendung, die Sie kostenlos herunterladen hinzufügen.

Unsere Anwendung hat keinerlei Verbindung zu oder mit den Supermärkten.


Dies ist keine offizielle Anwendung, sondern sie wurde für Hobbyzwecke entwickelt.

Sollte es Supermärkte geben, die nicht möchten, dass ihre Kataloge oder Broschüren veröffentlicht werden, dann können Sie uns darüber informieren, damit wir die Broschüren und Kataloge des jeweiligen Supermarktes unverzüglich von der Anwendung entfernen.

title: Klarna | Smoooth shopping
description:
Teemme shoppailusta smooothia. Klarnan avulla voit ostaa haluamasi nyt ja maksaa joustavasti silloin kun itse haluat. Klarna-sovellus tarjoaa yleiskuvan ostoksistasi. Voit maksaa ostoksesi yhdellä napsautuksella sekä pidentää vaivattomasti minkä tahansa ostoksesi maksuaikaa. Myös tuotteiden palauttaminen on helppoa ja vaivatonta.

MAKSA MITEN HALUAT.
Maksamisessa joustavuus on valttia. Tee ostoksia omilla ehdoillasi ja maksa miten haluat – maksa nyt, maksa myöhemmin tai pilko maksut.

TORKUTA MAKSUSI
Mikäli tarvitset lisäaikaa maksaa tilauksesi, voit helposti torkuttaa minkä tahansa tilauksen suoraan sovelluksessa.

KÄSITTELE MAKSUJASI.
Kaikki maksusi yhdessä sovelluksessa. Saat kattavan yleiskuvan kaikista ostoksistasi ja voit maksaa ne helposti sovelluksen kautta. Se on smooothia.

VASTAANOTA MUISTUTUKSIA
Älä koskaan unohda maksuasi. Pysy taloudessasi ajan tasalla aktivoimalla muistutusilmoitukset.

PALAUTUKSISTA ON TEHTY HELPPOJA
Teemme palautuksista vaivattomia. Merkitse sovelluksessa tuotteet, jotka aiot lähettää takaisin. Sinun ei tarvitse maksaa tuotteista, jotka palautat.

SEURAA TOIMITUKSIASI.
Saat välittömästi tiedon ostoksistasi ja voit seurata niiden kulkua kaupasta kotiovelle.

TERVETULOA PIMEÄLLE PUOLELLE.
Klarna-sovellukseen saa nyt Dark-tilan. Älä anna valon enää häiritä. Smoooth. 

OLEMME KÄYTETTÄVISSÄSI.
Ole yhteydessä meihin sovelluksen chatin välityksellä, mikäli tarvitset apua tai haluat antaa meille palautetta. Olemme täällä sinua varten. <3

You control the snake to eat as many pizzas as you can. Each pizza gives you points.
With points, you collect stars. There are 5⭐ stars for each level.

title: Nordea Mobile - Danmark
description:
Med mobilbanken kan du gøre alt det, du bruger banken til i hverdagen: overføre penge, tjekke din saldo, betale regninger, spærre dit betalingskort og meget, meget mere.

ENKEL OG INTUITIV
Design din egen forside. Du kan bl.a. vælge at fremhæve og navngive de konti, du bruger allermest, så du får et overblik over din daglige økonomi, der passer dig.
Scan og betal dine regninger med kameraet, overfør penge mellem dine konti eller til en ven, eller få et hurtigt overblik over dine investeringer og afkast – lige når det passer dig.
Log hurtigt på mobilbanken med NemID, fingeraftryk, ansigtsgenkendelse eller personlig kode. Du vælger selv.

TAG KONTROL OVER DINE KORT
Tilføj dine betalingskort til Google Pay, og lad pungen blive derhjemme. Hvis du senere glemmer pinkoden til et af dine kort, er det enkelt at se din kode direkte i appen. 
Mister du et af dine betalingskort, kan du nemt spærre kortet og åbne det igen, hvis kortet skulle dukke op. Hvis ikke, bestiller du nemt et nyt – klar til brug på få minutter.

Du kan som noget nyt minimere risikoen for svindel ved at begrænse, hvilke geografiske områder dit kort kan bruges i. Du kan også selv vælge, at dit kort ikke skal anvendes til internethandel. 

KONTAKT OS, SOM DET PASSER DIG BEDST
Du kan ringe eller chatte med os døgnet rundt alle årets dage. Du kommer hurtigst igennem, hvis du ringer eller skriver via mobilbanken. 

Vi håber, du får glæde af mobilbanken :-)

Giv os din feedback direkte i appen. Vi arbejder hele tiden på at gøre mobilbanken endnu bedre.

title: Ajaa Läpi Supermarket 3D Sim
description:
Toista ensimmäinen tulevaisuuden auton ostoksia kokemusta uusin Drive Thru Supermarket 3D simulaattori peli. Aja autolla läpi supermarket, ostoksia modernin ajaa läpi ostoskeskus. Park autoja edessä päivittäistavarakaupan hyllyt ja poimia kohteita haluat tehdä ostoksia supermarketissa.


Nauti interaktiivinen pelattavuus nokkela lainausmerkkejä ja vuoropuhelua. Aja talon autotallissa kohti supermarket ja ostaa tarvittavat kohdat päivällinen, lounas tai aamiainen. Opi useita reseptejä ja auttaa vaimonsa tekemään herkullista ruokaa keittiössä. Vauhtia ja ostoksia päivittäistavarat elintarvikkeita luettelosta. Ajaa läpi eri päivittäistavaroiden telineet ostaa tarvittavat tavarat. Futuristinen supermarket on erityinen telineet eri elintarvikkeita ja kotitalouksien elintarvikkeita. Ostaa perunoita tai porkkanoita, siirry vihanneksia telineeseen ja ostaa mangoja tai banaaneja, ajaa hedelmiä nurkkaan. Grand supermarket on rajoittamaton varasto päivittäistavaroiden poimia. Varmista, että teet ostoksia kaiken ennen kuin aika loppuu. Jälkeen ostoksia ajaa takaisin kotiin niin että päivällinen voidaan keittää. Ennen kuin lähdet ostoksia markkinoilla, maksaa laskun osoitteessa käteisellä counter ajon autoa.


Hauskaa Shop-in kanssa mukavin ja kätevä ostokokemus. Ajo ajaa läpi supermarket on jännittävä ja haastava. Ajo ajoneuvojen sisällä ostoskeskuksen tarvitsee korkean tarkkuuden. Ole varovainen ajaessasi ja pysäköinti auton lähellä hyllyt. Välttää lyömällä seisoo ja muut pysäköityjen autojen ostoskeskuksessa. Pysäköidä backwords ja pysähdy oikeaan asentoon. Vietä hauskaa tuntia ostoksilla ja päästä kassakone laskuri maksua. Seuraa signaaleja sisällä kaupungin supermarket. Reverse autoja huolellisesti välttää kaatuu ja Smashing. Flying auto supernopeasti sisällä Mart tulee olemaan suuria vaikeuksia. Kaupunki poliisi pidättää sinut aiheuttamisesta kaaos supermarkettia.


Ostaa vaatteita, kenkiä, ruokakauppa jne nousematta auton. Ole pro auton kuljettaja: istu ylellinen autoja ja vain jotta ylöspäin. Maksa lasku kassalla ja siirtää ajoneuvo pois kaupungista supermarket. Hämmästyttävän moderni ostoskeskus Lataa ilmaiseksi Drive Thru Supermarket 3D Simbest ajo simulointi peli.


Drive Thru Supermarket 3D Simulator Pelin ominaisuudet:
Useita auton ajo operaatioille kauppakeskus Plaza ostaa ruokaa tavaraa
Aja hämmästyttävä luksusautoja ja urheiluauto eri malleja
Realistinen supermarket sisustus ja suurkaupungin ympäristössä
Valtava osastojen tallentaa kaikenlaisia tuotteita
Rajoittamaton päivittäistavarakaupan kohteita suurissa elintarvikkeiden telineet animaatio
Luovasti suunniteltu interaktiivinen pelattavuuden nokkela lainausmerkit
Mukaansatempaava 3D-grafiikka ja mahtava äänet


Lataa Drive Thru Supermarket 3D simulaattori peli ja nauti ajo autoja kuin koskaan ennen.
