title: Betalingsservice
description:
Betal nye regninger og tilmeld fremtidige til Betalingsservice. Få overblik over din privatøkonomi og undgå ubehagelige rykkergebyrer – med Betalingsservice app’en får du ualmindeligt meget mere styr på dine regninger. 

Med Betalingsservice app’en kan du se alle dine betalingsaftaler ét sted, når som helst, hvor som helst. Og holde styr på faste udgifter som fx husleje, træning, tv, el, lån, støttebidrag og mobilabonnement. 

Du behøver ikke være kunde i en bestemt bank. Du kan bruge Betalingsservice app’en, hvis du har et dansk cpr.nr., en dansk bankkonto med tilslutningsaftale til Betalingsservice og NemID.

ANVENDELIGE KORT TIL FØRSTEGANGSBETALING:
• Dankort
• Visa/Dankort
• Visa
• Visa Electron
• Mastercard
• Maestro

KENDTE UDFORDRING
• Ved betalingsserviceaftaler tilknyttet en bankkonto, som du deler med andre, fx din ægtefælle kan du opleve, at du ikke kan få adgang til alle betalingsoplysningerne.


FÅ BETALINGSSERVICE – NÅR SOM HELST, HVOR SOM HELST
• Se hvilke regninger, du har betalt og hvad du skal betale. 
• Få det samlede overblik over alle dine faste betalingsaftaler – fra alle dine konti.
• Gem dine kortoplysninger (Dankort, Visa/Dankort, Visa, Visa Electron, Mastercard, Maestro) 
• Betal dine indbetalingskort (Dankort, Visa/Dankort, Visa, Visa Electron, Mastercard, Maestro)
• Tilmeld regninger til automatisk betaling – nemt og hurtigt.
• Modtag push beskeder i forbindelse med betalinger og tilmeldinger

BETAL OG TILMELD REGNINGER TIL BETALINGSSERVICE – NEMT OG HURTIGT
• Skan QR-koden eller OCR linjen på regningen – betal og tilmeld på max 2 minutter.
• Modtag push beskeder, når dine betalinger og aftaler er godkendt.
• Brug Dankort eller Visa/Dankort til førstegangsbetalingen 


SE ALLE DINE BETALINGER OG AFTALER – ÉT STED
• Se alle dine tidligere betalinger, måned for måned, flere år tilbage. 
• Se status og detaljer for hver enkelt betaling.
• Se alle dine faste betalingsaftaler.

FÅ OVERBLIK OVER DINE FASTE UDGIFTER – PÅ ET ØJEBLIK
• Se dine udgifter hen over året.
• Se, hvordan dine udgifter fordeler sig på fx bolig, forbrug, velgørenhed, forsyning, forsikring, a-kasse, transport, børn, undervisning, underholdning, medier, sundhed, lån, sport og kontingenter.
• Opret et budget og følg dit forbrug.
 
EKSTRA SIKKERHED OG SELVVALGT KODE
Første gang du bruger Betalingsservice app’en, skal du bruge dit NemID. Herefter kan du logge på med en 4-cifret PIN-kode, du selv vælger.
For at bruge app’en skal du have:
• Gyldigt dansk CPR.nr.
• Dansk bankkonto med tilslutningsaftale til Betalingsservice
• NemID
NemID giver dig adgang til hente dine betalingsoplysninger, og med NemID har du sikkerhed for, at kun du har adgang til dine data. Data du indtaster i app’en, sendes krypteret til Betalingsservice.

BEGRÆNSNINGER FOR FÆLLES KONTI
Er dine Betalingsserviceaftaler tilknyttet en bankkonto, som du deler med andre, fx din ægtefælle kan du opleve, at du ikke kan få adgang til alle betalingsoplysningerne.

INFORMATION OG INDSTILLINGER
Under indstillinger kan du se og redigere din konto, Dankortoplysninger, Push beskeder og personlige information. Du kan også se vilkår og ofte stillede spørgsmål.
Har du forslag til forbedringer, vil vi gerne høre fra dig på www.facebook.com/Betalingsservice.

title: Blackbaud MobilePay
description:
With Blackbaud MobilePay, you can accept and process credit card payments – such as for tickets, admission, and merchandise – through Blackbaud Merchant Services, anywhere with an Android phone or tablet. To process credit cards through your mobile phone or tablet, simply download the free application from the Play Store and request your complimentary credit card readers from Blackbaud. It’s that easy!

Blackbaud’s free app and readers help ease Point-of-Sale transactions. You pay the same low rate on every transaction, with no hidden or additional fees, regardless of the credit card used. Blackbaud MobilePay transactions automatically disburse and reconcile with your other Blackbaud Merchant Services transactions, so there’s no need for separate bank deposits. Also, Blackbaud MobilePay card readers encrypt credit card data to automatically secure your transactions.

title: mtv Suomi
description:
mtv tarjoaa suuren määrän kotimaisia ja ulkomaisia ohjelmia sekä uutislähetyksiä katseltavaksesi ilmaiseksi silloin, kun sinulle parhaiten sopii!

mtv-sovelluksella saat:

• Satoja ohjelmia ilmaiseksi silloin, kun sinulle parhaiten sopii.
• Suosikkiohjelmiesi uusimmat jaksot katseltaviksesi samaan aikaan, kun ne näytetään MTV3-, Sub- tai AVA-kanavilla. Osasta ohjelmista kaikki tai osa jaksoista julkaistaan mtv:ssä jo aamusta ennen tv-esitystä.
• Mahdollisuuden peilata katsomasi ohjelman televisioruudulle Chromecastin kautta

Tietoa mtv-palvelusta:

mtv-palvelun (eli entisen MTV Katsomon) ohjelmatarjontaan kuuluu kotimaisia ja ulkomaisia päivittäis- ja draamasarjoja, uutislähetyksiä, koko perheen viihdeohjelmia, puhutuimpia reality-ohjelmia ja paljon muuta.

Ohjelmat ovat katseltavissa mtv:ssä ohjelmasta riippuen yleensä 7-60 vuorokautta, mutta joskus jopa useamman vuoden ajan. Näet ohjelmatiedoista kuinka kauan yksittäisellä ohjelmalla on katseluaikaa jäljellä. Huomioithan, että osa ohjelmistamme on tekijänoikeussyistä katsottavissa vain Suomessa.

Ohjelmien katselu vaatii langattoman verkkoyhteyden. Ohjelmien kuvanlaatu määräytyy automaattisesti käytettävissä olevan verkkoyhteyden nopeuden perusteella. Suosittelemme käyttämään WLAN-yhteyttä silloin kun se on mahdollista. 
mtv:n käyttäminen edellyttää sisäänkirjautumista. Kirjauduttuasi sisään voit luoda listoja suosikkiohjelmistasi ja jatkaa katselua siitä mihin jäit, laitteesta riippumatta.Voit myös tilata sovellukseen ilmoituksen, kun suosikkisarjastasi on ilmestynyt uusi jakso.

mtv-sovellus on saatavilla myös Android TV -laitteisiin, joihin on asennettu Android 5.0 tai tätä uudempi käyttöjärjestelmäversio.

Heräsikö kysymyksiä? mtv-palvelun ohjeissa osoitteessa www.mtv.fi/ohjeet on vastaukset asiakkaiden yleisimpiin kysymyksiin sekä asiakaspalvelumme yhteystiedot. Ongelmatilanteessa löydät siis avun ohjeista ja tarvittaessa voit ottaa yhteyttä ripeään ja ystävälliseen asiakaspalveluumme.

Kirjaudu mtv-palveluun ja nauti ohjelmistamme milloin ja missä haluat, täysin ilmaiseksi!

title: Design Games Elisa Designer
description:
Hello girls! We are happy to dedicate this game to all the design games lovers. Have you ever dreamed to make your own dress? If the answer is yes then this design game will give you a little taste of what do you have to do when you want to become a designer. 
This design game has some simple steps that you have to follow in order to create you dream dress. 
The game starts when our character Elisa realize that she needs a new dress for the a special party so she decides to make one on her own. 
The second step that you have to make in order to design your dress is to find the correct parts of the dress and then we arrive at step number three. In this step you need to find the correct fabrics for your dress.
After that this design games continues with measurements. You will have to measure the shoulder length, upper body length, bust , hips and finish with out seam.  
The step that follows is the one where you need to draw the shapes with a pencil on the fabric and then cut it with the scissors. 
And like in all the design games out on the web , it comes the part where you need to sew the fabrics and complete this awesome dress. 
The game finish with some cool accessories that you can add to make this dress more fashionable and pick some shoes to be in accordance with the dress and then you are DONE!
Congratulations now you are a true fashion designer. 
Thank you for playing our design games . We look forward to hear your feedback!

title: Helsingin Sanomat
description:
Tervetuloa lukemaan Suomen parasta journalismia. 

Hesari kertoo kaiken olennaisen Suomesta ja maailmalta – uusimmista uutisista laajoihin reportaaseihin, henkeäsalpaavaan kuvajournalismiin ja tenhoaviin livelähetyksiin. Palkitut toimittajamme ja kirjeenvaihtajamme kutsuvat sinut matkalle kiinnostavimpiin ja puhutuimpiin paikkoihin ympäri maailman. 

HS tarjoaa näkökulmia hyvinvoinnista tieteeseen ja kulttuurista yhteiskuntaan. Seuraa Hesaria ja paranna maailmaasi. 

Lataa Hesarin maksuton sovellus ja lue kymmeniä uusia juttuja joka päivä, seuraa haluamiasi aiheita ja valitse juuri sinulle sopivat uutisilmoitukset HS:n uutisvirrasta – vaihtoehtoja on kaupunkikulttuurista hyvinvointiin ja päivän uutisotsikoista mielenkiintoisimpiin puheenvuoroihin.

title: DNA Arcade
description:
Life is written with only four letters A (Adenine), T (Thymine), G (Guanine) and C (Cytosine), and to transmit this information, the DNA strands must be used as a template and copied letter by letter. However, in the process of this replication, the same letters that are being copied are not written, but the letter of their complementary pair. These pairs are A-T and G-C. In this arcade biology game, the player must face time while copying a sequence of colors (representing the nitrogenous bases), but the copy must be with its complementary pairs.

---
This game is made by only one person, I hope you enjoy it! And if you find programming errors or something that does not work well for you, PLEASE, contact me by email to fix it.

descriptionHTML:
★ Supports your Local Device Storage as well as the most used Cloud Services!
★ Your photos are loaded quickly and displayed on an interative map
You can zoom in to see the exact position
★ The perfect photo gallery for travelers - Keep your memories alive like never before

High performance! Tested with more than 75,000 photos!

The free version is limited to 500 photos. Buying the pro version means: Unlimited photos for your local device storage, and up to 20k photos for the cloud. If 20k isn't enough for you (cloud), you can purchase multiple extra packs, that will increase the limit by 10k each.

You do not have to worry about your privacy. You photos are only cached locally, any home server communication, no analytics!

This app has many unique features. It helps you to find great spots again. You can navigate from location to location in chronological order.
You can share your Photos and Collages with friends.

✔ Recent Android versions are supported as example Android 8.0 Oreo, Android 9.0 Pie (2019) and Android 10 (Q)! It's even Android 11 ready!
✔ There is even an 3D Mode! Just use two fingers to switch to the 3D mode
✔ You have the possibility to view all EXIF information like the GPS position, a description and the rating. This information can also be changed and are stored inside the file, so other programs can read them
✔ You can choose if you want to see the satellite, hybrid or terrain view. Open street map (OSM, OpenStreetMap)

Features
★ Date: Your photos are automatically sorted by date taken
★ Location (PhotoMap): On a map you can see where you have taken the photos
★ Detailed view: One can of course look at the photos in whole size and possibly delete, share and view other information about it
★ Video playback
★ Explorer mode: In all views you can select between the grid view and the explorer/list view
★ Search: You can search your photos by using the name, folder, date, as was as for attractions, locations, countries or other interesting places (reverse geocoding)

Settings
★ Two color themes are actually implemented
★ You can change the number of columns, sort and group of every section
★ There are so many settings, I can't even list them all here!

More
★ GIF support
★ You can geo locate an image directly on the map
★ Zoom feature is available in the detail view. Tab to activate the Fullscreen mode
★ This app can be registered as default image viewer
★ Hidden Folders: Hide any folder you want in your gallery
★ Material design + features like the ei OS gallery
★ Erase EXIF: Delete all personal EXIF information from a photo

title: DNB
description:
DNB’s mobile app gives you a complete overview of your finances and access to the banking services you need with just a few clicks. Easy and convenient on-the-go.

We’ve upgraded our mobile bank with a modern and user-friendly design, in addition to several new, exciting features. In the mobile bank you can, among other things: 

•	swipe to make quick and easy payments and transfers
•	snap a picture and pay your bills with the invoice scanner
•	see your future balance after upcoming expenses
•	get an overview of your cards and accounts
•	log in with your fingerprint, if your mobile supports this
•	select the accounts you want displayed on your home page


We’ve also made it possible for you to check your account balance without logging into the app. DNB Balance Peek is a widget (mini program) that fetches your balance information from the app. Just add DNB Balance Peek to your mobile and you’ll be able to check your balance right from your Home screen or Lock screen. You’ll find more information about this in the app. 

DNB’s mobile bank makes it easier for you to carry out banking services in your everyday life. It will also offer a wide range of new features in the future. We will continuously upgrade our mobile bank, so that you, as a customer, at all times have access to the best solution.

All you need to do to get started is to download the app. Then login in with your BankdID, BankID on mobile or code device. If your phone supports fingerprint, you’ll be able to select this after your first login.

Download the app now and get access to the banking platform of the future from DNB!

You can be confident that DNB respects your privacy by protecting personal data, online traffic data and communications on our mobile services. General terms and Protection of personal privacy safeguard this and helps you understand how DNB uses and protects your information when using our mobile applications and websites.

title: Ancestry - Family History
description:
Discover where you came from through photos, stories, historical documents, and so much more. With the Ancestry® app you can explore and collect your family stories anytime, anywhere.

  • NEW - Now search for ancestors across 20+ billion historical records, photos, gravestone images, stories and more
  • Discover your genetic ethnicity, and make connections with living relatives, by taking an Ancestry DNA® test
  • With Ancestry Hints® get sent new automated discoveries about your ancestors; their life stories, their actual family photos, where they came from, languages they spoke, how they made a living and more 
  • Preserve you and your family’s information (photos, stories, life events, and more) in a single location so it can be preserved for generations to come 
  • Share your discoveries and collaborate with friends and family
  

Android Phone and Tablet Features:

  • Ancestry Hints® automatically finds records, photos, and stories about your family
  • In just a few taps create, edit, and add your family tree
  • Sync automatically with your Ancestry.com account 
  • Easily upload and preserve your family photos 
  • View your Ancestry DNA® ethnicity and DNA matches
  • Advanced search features so you can more easily find ancestors across our 20+ billion records.

title: Siirto – Käteinen kännykässä
description:
KUIN KÄTEINEN, MUTTA KÄNNYKÄSSÄ
Ei käteistä mukana? Ei hätää, Siirto on helppo ja vaivaton tapa hoitaa arjen pienet maksut suoraan pankkitililtäsi. Viikkoraha, jaettu ravintolalasku, kirpputorilöytö – maksu hoituu Siirrolla silmänräpäyksessä. 

SUOMESSA TEHTY – TURVALLINEN KÄYTTÄÄ
Siirto on suomalainen mobiilimaksusovellus, jossa kaikki käyttäjät on vahvasti tunnistettu. Voit käyttää sovellusta suomeksi, ruotsiksi, tai englanniksi. Alle 15-vuotiaat saavat sovelluksen käyttöön huoltajan hyväksynnällä. 

JO LÄHES MILJOONA KÄYTTÄJÄÄ
Rahan lähettämiseen tarvitset vain saajan puhelinnumeron. Syötä summa ja pyyhkäise, rahat siirtyvät välittömästi pankkitililtäsi toisen Siirto-käyttäjän pankkitilille. 

JAA YHTEINEN KULU
Ostitko yhteisen lahjan tai maksoitko ravintolaskun? Tai kenties ostit leffaliput ystävällesi? Siirrolla pyydät helposti rahaa toiselta käyttäjältä, ja seuraat avoinna olevia pyyntöjä. 

SEURAA TAPAHTUMIA VAIVATTOMASTI
Maksutapahtumat tallentuvat viestien tavoin keskusteluiksi, joista näet helposti sinun ja ystäväsi välisen maksuhistorian.

KÄTEVÄSTI QR KOODILLA
Siirrolla voit maksaa myös myyntipisteissä QR-koodilla. Lue myyjän QR-koodi ja vahvista maksu – valmista tuli! Kätevä tilanteissa, joissa et tunne käyttäjää, kuten kirpputorilla tai urheilutapahtuman myyjäisissä.

Lue lisää: www.nordea.fi/siirto

title: SpareBank 1 Mobilbank
description:
Mobilbankappen fra SpareBank 1 gir deg tilgang til de mest brukte bank- og forsikringstjenestene du trenger når du er på farten. I tillegg kan du på en enkel måte ta kontakt med oss.

I mobilbanken får du full oversikt over dine kontoer, kort, betalinger, sparing, lån og forsikringer – og du kan selvsagt bestille en rekke tjenester og produkter. Vi legger til nye tjenester fortløpende.

Appen inneholder også «Melde skade», reisekort og mulighet for å bestille verdivurdering av din bolig. 

Aktivering

Mobilbanken aktiveres med BankID. Deretter bruker du en selvlaget PIN eller fingeravtrykk for å logge inn.  

Gi oss ris og ros

Vi liker kommentarer og tilbakemeldinger fra deg for å kunne bli bedre. Ta kontakt med oss gjennom våre sosiale kanaler, kundesenteret eller skriv en kommentar i Google Play. 

Bli kunde

Er du ikke kunde hos oss, kan du enkelt bli kunde på www.sparebank1.no 

Tilganger og personvern

Vi bruker Google Analytics til å samle inn anonym statistikk om hvordan kundegrupper (ikke enkeltpersoner) bruker appen. Formålet med dette er å lage statistikk, som vi benytter til å forbedre appen. Eksempler på hva statistikken gir oss svar på er:

•  Hvor mange som bruker ulike telefontyper og operativsystemer?
•  Hvor mange som logger seg inn fra ulike land?
•  Hvor mange som bruker de ulike tjenestene i appen?

I de tilfeller Google Analytics benyttes, blir informasjonen om din bruk lagret på Googles servere i USA. Informasjonskapselen samler blant annet inn IP-adressen din, men SpareBank 1 har valgt å legge inn en kode som fjerner de siste sifrene fra IP-adressen din før informasjonen lagres av Google. Dette gjør at analyseverktøyet kan anslå brukerens geografiske plassering, men adressen kan ikke benyttes for å identifisere den enkelte bruker.

Informasjonskapslene inneholder ikke personopplysninger.
descriptionHTML:
Mobilbankappen fra SpareBank 1 gir deg tilgang til de mest brukte bank- og forsikringstjenestene du trenger når du er på farten. I tillegg kan du på en enkel måte ta kontakt med oss.

I mobilbanken får du full oversikt over dine kontoer, kort, betalinger, sparing, lån og forsikringer – og du kan selvsagt bestille en rekke tjenester og produkter. Vi legger til nye tjenester fortløpende.

Appen inneholder også «Melde skade», reisekort og mulighet for å bestille verdivurdering av din bolig.

Aktivering

Mobilbanken aktiveres med BankID. Deretter bruker du en selvlaget PIN eller fingeravtrykk for å logge inn.  

Gi oss ris og ros

Vi liker kommentarer og tilbakemeldinger fra deg for å kunne bli bedre. Ta kontakt med oss gjennom våre sosiale kanaler, kundesenteret eller skriv en kommentar i Google Play.

Bli kunde

Er du ikke kunde hos oss, kan du enkelt bli kunde på www.sparebank1.no

Tilganger og personvern

Vi bruker Google Analytics til å samle inn anonym statistikk om hvordan kundegrupper (ikke enkeltpersoner) bruker appen. Formålet med dette er å lage statistikk, som vi benytter til å forbedre appen. Eksempler på hva statistikken gir oss svar på er:

•  Hvor mange som bruker ulike telefontyper og operativsystemer?
•  Hvor mange som logger seg inn fra ulike land?
•  Hvor mange som bruker de ulike tjenestene i appen?

I de tilfeller Google Analytics benyttes, blir informasjonen om din bruk lagret på Googles servere i USA. Informasjonskapselen samler blant annet inn IP-adressen din, men SpareBank 1 har valgt å legge inn en kode som fjerner de siste sifrene fra IP-adressen din før informasjonen lagres av Google. Dette gjør at analyseverktøyet kan anslå brukerens geografiske plassering, men adressen kan ikke benyttes for å identifisere den enkelte bruker.

Informasjonskapslene inneholder ikke personopplysninger.

title: Mobile Bank UK – Danske Bank
description:
The new Danske Mobile Bank app is here - you can bank on it!
Our brand new mobile app gives you a simple way to control your money, 24 hours a day.

The new app is:
Simpler - Transfer money quickly and easily
Smarter - Block and unblock your card in seconds
Safer - Added security with facial or fingerprint logon

Use it to check your accounts and balances, send money through Paym, view your statements, send us secure messages, and much more.

Getting started is easy
If you are a personal customer (aged 13 years and over) of Danske Bank in the UK using eBanking you can:

1.Download the app
2.Log on using your Electronic Signature
3.You’re ready to go!

If you haven’t registered for eBanking, please do so by going to www.danskebank.co.uk/waystobank.

Enjoy!

title: CircleDNA
description:
Unlock your DNA with Circle! The Circle Exome Series has been designed for those who take health and wellness seriously. Understand everything your genes can tell you about your:
• Cancer risk
• Disease risk
• Family planning
• Diet and nutrient needs
• Skin
• Stress & Sleep
+ many more!

Every test comes with a complimentary 30-min phone consultation with a genetics-trained health coach and/or a genetic counsellor. 

Use of services require purchasing a kit and submitting a saliva sample using the DNA Collection Kit provided. You can easily create an account, register your DNA kit, and track the progress of your sample. Once you get your results, open the app to see all your reports!

In the app, you can also:
• Discover actionable insights that help you take control of your well-being so that you can live a happier, healthier life.
• Get the latest scientific studies and resources.
• Easily manage your family members in one account.

Haluatko seurata tilauksiasi Kiinasta tai muualta maailmasta? Kokeile uudistunutta 17trackia! Voit seurata yli 200 kuljetusyhtiön lähetyksiä ilmaiseksi ja ilman mainoksia.

17track on 17track.netin, joka on suurin maailmanlaajuinen lähetyste seurantasivusto, virallinen sovellus. Sovellus tukee yli 170 kuljetusyhtiötä (esim. Kiinan posti, Kiinan EMS,  jne.) ja lisäksi monia pikakuljetusyhtiöitä. Myös monet verkkokauppayhtiöiden käyttämät logistiikkakumppanit ovat tuettuja .Ennen sovelluksen lataamista voit halutessasi kokeilla myös selainversiota - www.17track.net

* Saat ilmoituksen, kun lähetyksen tila muuttuu
* Päivitä kaikki seurantanumerot vetämällä alas
* Kuljetusyhtiön automaattinen tunnistus
* Kopioi ja jaa seurantalinkkejä ja -tuloksia helposti
* Tunnista seurantanumerot tekstin seasta
* Anna nimi lähetyksille
* Lue lähetysten viiva- tai QR-koodeja
* Useita eri kieliä
* Seurannan tulosten käännösmahdollisuus
* Kotinäytön pienoisohjelma
* Vaakasuora näyttö tabletteja varten
* Ilmoitukset, kun tila muuttuu
* Synkronointi eri laitteiden välillä pilvipalvelun avulla
* Kirjautuminen Ja paljon muuta...

Jos teet ostoksia netissä, 17track on sovellus, jota ei kannata jättää asentamatta. Lataa 17track, niin pysyt ajan tasalla kaikesta mitä ostat netistä.
Jos sinulla on ehdotuksia tai kohtaat ongelmia sovelluksen käytössä, ota meihin yhteyttä lähettämällä sähköpostia osoitteeseen feedback@17track.net
Seurantaan liittyvissä kysymyksissä lähetä sähköpostia osoitteeseen serv@17track.net

title: Pharmaca Fennica
description:
Pharmaca Fennica on terveydenhuollon ammattilaisten luottama palvelu lääketietojen hakuun.

Sovelluksen avulla sinulla on ajantasaiset lääketiedot helposti käytettävissäsi. Sovelluksessa voit:

- Hakea kauppanimellä, vaikuttavalla aineella, käyttöaiheella, yrityksen nimellä tai Vnr-numerolla
- Hakea lukemalla lääkepakkauksen viivakoodin
- Valita ennustavan haun avulla oikean hakusanan
- Rajata hakua antoreitin perusteella
- Selata kattavia Pharmaca Fennica -selosteita otsikoittain
- Tallentaa usein käyttämiesi lääkkeiden tiedot myöhempää tarkastelua varten
- Siirtyä yhdellä napauksella suoraan haluamasi lääkkeen tietoihin Tallennetut-valikosta
- Ottaa yhteyttä lääkkeen markkinoijaan
- Käyttää sovellusta ja hakea lääketietoja myös ilman verkkoyhteyttä
- Selata lääketurvatiedotteita ja riskienhallintamateriaaleja

Sovellus lataa ensimmäisellä käyttökerralla lääketietokannan laitteen muistiin. Sen jälkeen voit käyttää mobiilisovellusta myös ilman verkkoyhteyttä. Jos sovellus on käyttämättä pitkähkön ajan, niin laite päivittää lääketietokannan uusimman version käynnistyksen yhteydessä.

Sovelluksen tuottaa Lääketietokeskus Oy ja se pohjautuu Pharmaca Fennica Lääketietokantaan. Pharmaca Fennica on toiminut lääkkeen määräämiseen ja toimittamiseen oikeutettujen terveydenhuollon ammattilaisten luotettavana työkaluna yli 40 vuoden ajan.

title: DNA+
description:
Thông tin di truyền sẽ cho bạn hiểu rõ về sức khoẻ, tính trạng, tình trạng thể chất của mình. DNA+ là ứng dụng chăm sóc sức khoẻ toàn diện dựa trên kết quả xét nghiệm di truyền. Với DNA+ bạn có thể:
        - Xem hồ sơ di truyền cá nhân của bạn và những người thân yêu trong gia đình.
        - Giúp sàng lọc ung thư di truyền, phân tích nguy cơ các bệnh mãn tính và 7000+ bệnh.
        - Giúp quản lý và theo dõi các nguy cơ gây bệnh.
        - Khám phá hơn 80+ tính trạng tiềm ẩn trong bạn.
        - Truy cập cơ sở dữ liệu bênh học tiếng việt với hơn 7000+ bệnh.
        - Luôn luôn được cập nhật dữ liệu y khoa mới nhất.
        - Dễ dàng theo dõi tiến độ phân tích xét nghiệm của bạn.

title: e-Boks.dk
description:
With e-Boks you can access your mail digitally and securely from both companies and public authorities, anywhere and anytime. 

Our app provides you with a range of options to organize your mail. But e-Boks is much more than just a digital mailbox:

- Sign documents digitally. The documents are easily signed using NemID and saved in e-Boks.
- Pay bills. Pay your bills directly in e-Boks. Pay with creditcard or Betalingsservice. 
- e-Boks supports a multi-level folder structure unlike any other digital mailboxes out there, allowing you to organize your mail in a perfect tree structure.
- Mail management at your fingertips. Just swipe right to mark a message as read, or swipe left to archive.
- Read and manage mail that others have given you access to.
- Upload important personal documents. e-Boks is like an online bank vault, which allows you to store everything from mortgage deeds and birth certificates to photographs of your valuables for insurance claims.

We are also introducing e-Boks Plus. Here you can access a range of services which are designed to make your everyday life easier and more convenient. You decide which services you want to add, and you always have full control over the content. We are continuously adding new services and you are invited to share feedback and submit ideas to e-Boks Plus through the app.

It is easy to get started. You simply log-on as you are used to. If you are new to e-Boks we recommend creating a user with your NemID to get access to all features of the app.

title: Anatomyou VR | Human Anatomy
description:
Anatomyou VR is an educational mobile application that presents human anatomy to the user from a different perspective. 
Using virtual reality, the user becomes part of the anatomy in an immersive way, being able to navigate along anatomical structures: circulatory, respiratory, digestive, urinary, lacrimal and female reproductive system. 
It offers free of charge access to some navigation routes in almost any of the mentioned systems. Additional purchasable content is offered in an in-app store section of the application.
Anatomyou VR can be used in two different modes: Virtual Reality and Fullscreen.
In Virtual Reality mode, mobile device (smartphone) must be inserted in a virtual reality gadget to enjoy a fully immersive experience. User can interact with navigation controls and anatomical information elements by aiming them.
Although Anatomyou VR provides the best experience when used in Virtual Reality mode, the user can also enjoy and learn with this mobile application in fullscreen mode, without the needs of a virtual reality gadget.

title: Telia Påfyll
description:
Velkommen til den enkleste måten å lade et Telia Kontantkort på. Nå kan du lade ditt eget, en venns eller familien sine kontantkort fra Telia. Du trenger ikke å være Telia kontantkortkunde for å bruke Telia Påfyll. I Telia Påfyll kan du kjøpe både Smart Kontant og Kronepåfyll. Du betaler med bank- eller kredittkort. Når du registrerer deg kan du lagre ditt betalingskort og de kontantkortnummer du lader oftest. Det gjør påfyllet enda raskere og enklere.
Du registrerer deg med ditt mobilnummer og logger deretter inn med en pinkode du selv velger. Som forelder kan du lagre numrene til barna dine for enkelt påfyll. Du vil kunne se saldo og ladehistorien på de numre du har lagret. Det gir deg god oversikt over kostnadene ved ditt kontantkort. 
Hvis du har spørsmål eller dersom du opplever at ting ikke fungerer ber vi deg vennligst ta kontakt med Telia kundeservice på telefon: 05050, eller på http://Telia.no/kontakt-kundesenter. Hilsen Telia

title: Tattoodo - löydä seuraava tatuointisi
description:
Tattoodo tarjoaa sinulle tatuoinnin ystävien maailmanlaajuisen yhteisön ja suurimman tatuointimallien, tatuoijien ja kauppojen kokoelman. 

On mahdotonta olla inspiroitumatta!  

Tattoodo -sovelluksella voit: 

- ladata ja jakaa omia tatuointejasi
- tallentaa suosikkitatuointimalleja
- luoda parhaiden tyylien kokoelman
- tutustua maailman lahjakkaimpiin taiteilijoihin, seurata heitä ja ottaa heihin yhteyttä
- saada viimeisimmät tatuointitrendit kuvin, artikkelein ja videoin
- etsiä parhaat tatuointikaupat
- ottaa yhteyttä kauppoihin ja taiteilijoihin lähelläsi


Tatuoijat ja tatuointikaupat
Tattoodo-sovellusta käyttää jo 60 tuhatta tatuoijaa - älä missaa tätä! 

Kasvata liiketoimintaasi Tattoodon avulla: 

- Esittele kuviasi
- Pidä yhteyttä miljoonien potentiaalisten asiakkaiden kanssa
- Katso muiden taiteilijoiden töitä
- Kasvata seuraajapohjaasi
- Inspiroidu
- Hanki näkyvyyttä
- Hanki enemmän varauksia

Tarjoamme sinulle foorumin, jossa voit tehostaa liiketoimintaasi ja esitellä lahjakkuuttasi - loppu riippuu sinusta! 

Meillä on jo 20 miljoonaa kuukausittaista käyttäjää globaalissa yhteisössä, johon kuuluu taiteilijoita, kauppoja ja keräilijöitä. Tattoodo on sovellus tatuointitaiteen kehittämiseen ja arvostamiseen. Haluamme jakaa maailman parhaat tatuoinnit kanssasi! 

Lataa Tattoodo nyt!

title: Bake Pizza Delivery Boy: Pizza Maker Games
description:
Little baking chefs get ready for amazing fast food cooking games and cook finger licking treats for your customers. This good pizza maker food shop has lots of adventures of junk food games. Lots of hidden surprises of baking food restaurants are waiting for you.

Do you love to play pizza making baking games then enjoy the adventure of fast food maker with home delivery fun. Become a motorbike driver, pack the order and have the fun of becoming a delivery boy. The baking chef can enjoy fast food delivery also on vans. Get enjoyment from by riding the different vehicles of your choice. 

This good pizza maker game also has another surprise for little chefs. Let's enjoy the city bike racing fun. Drive fast and become the winner of this exciting moto race. These kids cooking games have so many interesting activities for you.

Three amazing modes give the endless fun of pizza maker delivery games and bike racing. In free mode, the baking chef is free to experiment with lots of tasty ingredients to make perfect fast food. Make the dough and many exciting shapes are there to make. Cook a very tasty sauce. Choose the topping from many items like veggies, cheese, meat, chicken and fish. Enjoy this fast food making kitchen games by making four kinds of delicious food. 

In the time interval mode customers will order yummy fast food. Take their orders and start your job of bake pizza delivery. Pick the vehicle of your choice and be the fast delivery driver. 

In the racing mode a pizza bike driver will face a race for delivery. When food is ready then your moto race will start with another delivery boy. Different types of motorbikes, vans and AI cars will also help the bike delivery driver to deliver the order within the timeline. 

Don’t waste time! Hurry up customers are calling you….

title: DNAApp: DNA sequence analyzer
description:
*In line with Android OS changes, please access local files using ES File Explorer, which will root the drive/SD cards. You will need to go in to ES File Explorer to perform the rooting first. 

This is the first android app that allows for the opening and analysis of DNA sequencing files - ab1. It includes handy tools such as "Reverse Complement", "Jump to", fast and end scrolling, "Chromatogram adjustments", amino acid translations, "export to fasta", and "searching for segment" function. 

When used in combination with other zip apps, and also web-tools, this app allows you to analyze, and also determine the quality of your sequencing files.

This app works with cloud storage access to your sequencing files.

**Please note that this app is only compatible with Android version 4 and above.**

Please cite: Bioinformatics Journal doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btu525

This app is a product of the Antibody & Product Development Lab, Translational Research Division, Bioinformatics Institute, Agency for Science, Technology, and Research, Singapore. 
Creators are: Mr NGUYEN Phi Vu, and Dr Samuel KE GAN.

title: MobilePay MyShop
description:
MobilePay MyShop has everything you need to offer your customers simple payments via MobilePay. 

With the free MyShop app, you can turn your phone into a payment terminal without any additional hardware. The app enables you to easily manage payments in all of your stores and gives you access to a complete overview of your day-to-day transactions. Combined with the online MobilePay administration portal, MyShop gives you the most simple and flexible payment solution on the market.

FEATURES

-Turns your phone into a payment terminal
-Enables contactless mobile payments without any additional hardware
-Enables you to request money from customers via Bluetooth or a QR code
-Gives you a complete overview of your sales in all stores
-Automatically notifies you when you receive payments

HOW DO I GET STARTED?

To start using the MyShop app you only need to sign up your business to MobilePay MyShop through our administration portal.

title: One
description:
Den nye OneCall-appen er her!
 
Som OneCall-kunde får du bedre kontroll over mobilhverdagen din! Du får detaljert oversikt over alle abonnement du administrerer og har full kontroll på kostnadene dine til enhver tid.  For kunder med Familiepakka gir appen deg veldig enkelt oversikt over familiens totale mobilbruk, og du kan enkelt administrere de enkelte medlemmene i familien rett fra appen.
 
Noe av det du kan gjøre i appen:
- Se hvor mye data du har igjen
- Se hvor mye TaMedData du har
- Kjøpe datapakker
- Slå av og på sperrer
- Se dine kostnader
 
Kjekt å vite!
Appen vår er selvsagt gratis, du må ha mobildata eller Wifi-tilgang for å bruke alle tjenestene i appen.
 
Appen er under utvikling, og vi vil fylle på med ny funksjonalitet fortløpende. Sørg for å holde appen oppdatert for å ha tilgang til den nyeste funksjonaliteten.
 
Ris og ros!
Gi oss gjerne feedback på appen ved å trykke på innstillings-ikonet i appen, eller ved å sende oss en e-post til kundeservice@onecall.no

title: Hot 🍕Pizza Factory - Pizza Cooking Game
description:
Hey, have you ever tried to cook pizza at home? Yes, then you've fun adventure in this Free Hot Pizza Factory - Cooking game! Today you'll manage the Pizza Cooking and delivery service in Pizza Factory game. Now make the delicious pizza and deliver it to the pizza shops.

Create your own delicious pizza using your creativity - choose from a huge range of ingredients and create the pizza that you like most. Every kids and adults loves to eat pizzas. You play the role of chef and cook the superb pizzas in Hot Pizza Factory - Cooking game.

Start pizza cooking by making pizza dough paste using eggs, flour, salt, water and other various ingredients and after that, just like any expert factory operator, start operating automated machines to pour the paste into them and making dough out of them. Making pizza in this pizza maker game is quite easy as you will be using machines to help you out. Dough will pass through a machine you will be using its controls to make a flat base of your yummy and delicious pizza. 

Assembly line will bake the pizza bread and take it to a specific place, where you will be adding hot chili, mayonnaise sauce, vegetables, chicken, and other kind of organic food types just like you do in burgers, sandwiches and hotdog making restaurant game. After going through pizza packaging you will drive the pizza truck to deliver hot & crispy pizza to the restaurants and pizza shops.

Download and play the most amazing & delicious pizza cooking game on you device with your family!

title: minube: travel planner & guide
description: ​★🏆 New! minube enters the apps hall of fame. The Google Team rewards minube with the Editors' Choice Badge in recognition of its quality, excellent design and innovative functionalities.★​ ​★🏆 2015: minube is named one of Google's 50 Best Apps of the year, for the third year in a row.★​ ​★🏆 2014: minube is named one of Google's 50 Best Apps of the year, for the second year in a row.★​ ​★🏆 2013: minube is named one of Google's 50 Best Apps of the year.★​ minube is travel planning app & travel organizer that lets you find vacation ideas, save favorite places in lists, and create your own travel itinerary & tourist guide. Minube is an app that lets you discover the best places around the world, all recommended by real travelers. Discover interesting places to visit in your own city or create your own personalized travel guides and save them to use offline during your vacation. The best part is that when your trip is done, the minube app will automatically create beautiful photo galleries of all the places you visited. Here’s how the minube app can help you with your travels: Deciding on where to take your next vacation On minube, you’ll find over 2 million tourist attractions, restaurants, and hotels around the world, all recommended by our community of over 1.5 million real travelers. Find expert lists by topic like the world’s best scuba diving locations or the cheapest cities to visit in Europe, or use our Inspiration tool to discover destinations using filters like color, distance from home, and more. Planning your trip Once you’ve decided on where to go, minube will help you unlock the best of the destination. Discover lists created by expert locals with themes like the best tapas restaurants in Barcelona or the most spectacular castles to visit in Germany. Or, read recommendations from real travelers and save your favorite places to see, eat, and stay into your own travel guides which you can then download and use offline during your vacation. During your trip The minube app can also help you during the trip itself. Use the app to discover restaurants and tourist attractions near your location, see the exact location of places you want to visit, or discover recommendations and lists about the place you’re visiting. Don’t forget that you can create your own travel guides and use them offline wherever you are. When you’ve finished traveling Finally, your trips don’t end when you get home. Minube helps you relive your favorite travel moments again and again! If you have GPS activated on your phone’s camera, the minube app can detect all of the photos from your trip and organize them into beautiful photo galleries complete with maps and travel dates. Not only is it a lovely reminder of your trip, it’s also perfect to share with your friends and family. Want to learn more about minube? Follow us on Facebook → https://www.facebook.com/minube Follow us on Twitter → https://twitter.com/minubeapp Why do we need these permissions? U+1F64B Identity: So you can create an account and enter into minube and enjoy a more thorough travel-planning experience. Location: To find tourist attractions, restaurants, and hotels near you and get directions to local points of interest. Internet: To connect to the minube platform and discover thousands of new places and destinations around the world.
descriptionHTML:
​★🏆 New! minube enters the apps hall of fame. The Google Team rewards minube with the Editors' Choice Badge in recognition of its quality, excellent design and innovative functionalities.★​

​★🏆 2015: minube is named one of Google's 50 Best Apps of the year, for the third year in a row.★​

​★🏆 2014: minube is named one of Google's 50 Best Apps of the year, for the second year in a row.★​

​★🏆 2013: minube is named one of Google's 50 Best Apps of the year.★​

minube is travel planning app & travel organizer that lets you find vacation ideas, save favorite places in lists, and create your own travel itinerary & tourist guide.

Minube is an app that lets you discover the best places around the world, all recommended by real travelers. Discover interesting places to visit in your own city or create your own personalized travel guides and save them to use offline during your vacation. The best part is that when your trip is done, the minube app will automatically create beautiful photo galleries of all the places you visited.

Here’s how the minube app can help you with your travels:

Deciding on where to take your next vacation
On minube, you’ll find over 2 million tourist attractions, restaurants, and hotels around the world, all recommended by our community of over 1.5 million real travelers. Find expert lists by topic like the world’s best scuba diving locations or the cheapest cities to visit in Europe, or use our Inspiration tool to discover destinations using filters like color, distance from home, and more.

Planning your trip
Once you’ve decided on where to go, minube will help you unlock the best of the destination. Discover lists created by expert locals with themes like the best tapas restaurants in Barcelona or the most spectacular castles to visit in Germany. Or, read recommendations from real travelers and save your favorite places to see, eat, and stay into your own travel guides which you can then download and use offline during your vacation.

During your trip
The minube app can also help you during the trip itself. Use the app to discover restaurants and tourist attractions near your location, see the exact location of places you want to visit, or discover recommendations and lists about the place you’re visiting. Don’t forget that you can create your own travel guides and use them offline wherever you are.

When you’ve finished traveling
Finally, your trips don’t end when you get home. Minube helps you relive your favorite travel moments again and again! If you have GPS activated on your phone’s camera, the minube app can detect all of the photos from your trip and organize them into beautiful photo galleries complete with maps and travel dates. Not only is it a lovely reminder of your trip, it’s also perfect to share with your friends and family.

Want to learn more about minube?

Follow us on Facebook → https://www.facebook.com/minube
Follow us on Twitter → https://twitter.com/minubeapp

Why do we need these permissions? U+1F64B

Identity: So you can create an account and enter into minube and enjoy a more thorough travel-planning experience.

Location: To find tourist attractions, restaurants, and hotels near you and get directions to local points of interest.

Internet: To connect to the minube platform and discover thousands of new places and destinations around the world.

title: Domino’s Pizza Caribbean
description:
Conveniently order Domino’s from anywhere on your Android phone and tablet. Build your Domino's pizza just the way you like it or choose one of our pre-built pizzas. Add items from the rest of our robust menu. And with the Domino’s Tracker ® you can follow your order from the moment you place it until it’s out for delivery, dine-in, carryout or pickup.

The Domino's Pizza Caribbean App currently supports the following countries - Aruba, Bahamas, Cayman Islands, Dominican Republic, Puerto Rico, St. Kitts, St. Lucia and St. Maarten.

FEATURES:
· Create a Domino's Pizza Profile to easily access to your saved info and recent orders (not required)
· Order faster than ever by creating an Easy Order!
· Use Domino’s Tracker notifications to follow your order until it’s out for delivery or ready for pickup!

title: TekstiTV
description:
✔️ Yhteensopiva Yle:n 17.3.2020 uusitun teksti-tv järjestelmän kanssa

Teksti-TV löytyy nyt kätevästi mobiiliappina. Mukana YLE:n tekstitv sekä Maikkarin teksti-tv palvelu. Ylen sivut 100-899. MTVn sivut 100-700. Klassinen laatupalvelu uutis- ja  urheilunälkään kätevässä sovelluksessa. Lataa helppokäyttöinen ja ilmainen appi sekä aloita mutkaton Tekstiteevee selailu nyt heti. Teksti-TV:n ulkoasu mukailee tietoisesti ja kunnioittaa retrotyylillään klassista kaikille tuttua teksti-tv olemusta.

Puhelinta kääntämällä vaaka-asentoon sovellus tunnistaa responsiivisesti asennon ja venyttää tekstitv:n koko ruudun kokoiseksi, jolloin tekstin lukeminen helpottuu huomattavasti ihmisille, joilla on näköaistin kanssa rajoitteita. Selailu onnistuu nyt myös swaippaamalla.

Selostusominaisuudella voit myös kuunnella sivun sisältöä lausuttuna. Sovelluksen käyttöliittymä on selkeä ja turhat käyttöä hidastavat tilpehöörit on karsittu pois. Sovellus ilmoittaa käyttäjilleen uusista ja päivittyneistä tekstitv uutisista ilmoitusten avulla, jotka voi halutessaan kytkeä pois.

Sivuja sekä alisivuja voit selailla helposti näppäimillä ja pääsivun voit halutessasi valita numeronäppäimillä. Sovellus on nopea ja löytää valitsemasi sivun heti. Useat käyttäjät ovat huomanneet tämän sovelluksen monet hyödyt ja ovat siirtyneet käyttämään ainoastaan Teksti-TV Suomea tekstitv-sovelluksenaan. Appi on todella kevyt akulle.

"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ - Paras teksti tv appi" - Mathias Ekholm
"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ - Hyvä Teksti TV appi" - Robert Smith
"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ - Hyvä ohjelma" - Markus Kaunisto

👍 YLE ja Maikkari
👍 Helppo käyttää
👍 YLE sivut 100-899
👍 MTV sivut 100-700
👍 Nopea sovellus
👍 Kevyt asennus
👍 Selostus
👍 100% ilmainen
👍 Ei nuuski käyttäjätietojasi tai olinpaikkaasi
👍 Ei vaadi tilejä tai kirjautumisia

Teksti-TV appi ei vaadi kirjautumista ja ei kerää käyttäjätietojasi. Sovellus on kevyt puhelimen akulle ja ei pyöri käynnistämättä taustalla. Teksti-TV hakee tiedot saumattomasti ja on aina ajan tasalla. Ota tästä helppo ilmainen appi käyttöön heti!

title: Gizmo VR Video Player: 360 Virtual Reality Videos
descriptionHTML:
Gizmo VR Player: 360 Virtual Reality Videos

How about getting your hands on one of vr apps with a pro level virtual reality player? An App that integrates with everything works great and is simple to use? Here’s the good news: Your new state of the art VR Media Player is now a reality with GizmoVR!

As you may know the Virtual Reality Headset you choose is actually less important than the player software App you run on it. With so many terrific Android devices available, many early adopters have had to suffer through a mess of 360 video player apps that failed to deliver what was needed. GizmoVR solves all that for free and offers you a robust set of features that are way ahead of any other App on the market right now.

GizmoVR Features:
❶ Integrated browser;
❷ Support of all stereo formats with side by side and over under frame packing;
❸ Media library with an option to add selected folders into favorites;
❹ Playback from YouTube;
❺ Automatic frame packing detection when files are run from the local storage;
❻ One click start from the browser;
❼ Integrated download manager;
❽ Flexible playback settings;
❾ Automatic pause if headset removed;
❿ VR player can be dragged;
⓫ Cinematic mode (curved or flat screen);
⓬ Control the app with a gaze in the hands-free mode;
⓭ Supported video formats: 2D/360°/180°.

GizmoVR is the next era virtual reality movie player offerring an entirely integrated browser that comes in handy for navigation or online surfing within the App itself, so it is far more convenient than other virtual reality apps.

Enjoy the versatility of GizmoVR with the full support of all stereo video formats including side-by-side and over-under frame packing, as well as all the traditional video formats. Get the best and most immersive VR POV from the only player truly capable of displaying 2D, 3D, 180-degree VR or fully encompassing 360° VR experiences and putting you right in the middle of all the action!

The GizmoVR media library allows you to add selected folders to your favorites for easy access to your preferred content with just a click or two on the headset itself.

title: VR Theater for Cardboard
description:
=== CAPTATIO BENEVOLENTIAE

There is no company or money of sorts behind this app: it's something I do in my spare time. If you like it, consider leaving a review or at least rating it.

Riccardo

=== SALES PITCH

Are you waiting for the perfect media player in proper VR? 

Give this one a try, while you keep waiting!

Sporting great features, like:

• plenty of bugs 
• sub-par graphics 
• incomplete and out of date instructions
• clumsy controls
• limited features

title: ASDA
description:
ASDA’s FREE± grocery shopping app lets you shop for groceries on the go. Get all the amazing in-store offers & easily book a delivery or use our Click & Collect service.
 
Grocery shopping made easy   
Shop your way: Available on all devices on the move. 
Scan items at home: Running out of something? Build your shopping list quickly and easily.  
Create shopping lists: Organise your shop to save time when you next shop using the FREE± Asda App.  
Shopped in-store before? : Transfer your favourite items on your receipt into your online basket. Clever!
Find your nearest store: By turning on-location services, you can locate your nearest store wherever you are.  
 
With the ASDA groceries shopping app, you can: 
 
- Shop the full grocery range available in our stores 
- Book, amend or cancel your order while on the go 
- Quickly add favourites and Shopping List items to your trolley 
- Browse special offers and rollbacks 
- Find items using voice search or barcode scanner 
- Discover recipes; add ingredients straight to your trolley or Shopping List in one tap 
- Buy an ASDA Delivery Pass for savings on delivery charges 
- Find nearby ASDA stores; view store hours, and get directions.
- Let us know you’re on your way. We’ll make sure your shopping is ready to collect when you arrive^

Here are the permissions the app needs, and what we use them for: 
- ‘Identity’ - used to securely save your login details to your phone

title: Ludo All Star- Play Online Ludo Game & Board Games
description: Ludo is an online strategy board game for two to four players & dice game that will revive your childhood memories. Ludo is a board game played between friends, family & kids. Ludo game, a simpler version of another Indian cross and circle game called Chopat, Chaupur, Pachisi or Parcheesi is a classic strategy board & dice game played by 2 or 4 players. Players roll a dice and race their four tokens from start to finish according to the dice roll. Along with the usual gameplay, all new online ludo games, Ludo All Star has come up with an interesting twist that will make you a lodo king game. The game also has a Raid Mode, which makes the lado star game more interesting. Get ready for the toughest battle with the ludo Online game against three friends of you with the most classic board game. Classic Ludo game is also going by different names & variations in different regions like लूडो,Uckers, Griniaris, Fia, Cờ cá ngựa, Petits Chevaux (Little Horses),Ki nevet a végén, برسي (Barjis/Barjees),Fei Xing Qi' (China),Parqués (Colombia),Barjis / Bargis (Palestine),Griniaris (Greece),Mens-erger-je-niet (the Netherlands),Parchís or Parkase (Spain),Le Jeu de Dada,Barjis(s) / Bargese (Syria),Pachîs (Persia/Iran),da' ngu'a ('Vietnam'),ludo chakka ( indian village),Parqués (Colombia),đá ngựa (Vietnam),Fei Xing Qi' (China),Parcheesi (North America),Parchís (Spain),Mensch ärgere Dich nicht (Germany),Non t'arrabbiare (Italy),Chińczyk (Poland),Reis ümber maailma (Estonia),Fia-spel or Fia med knuff (Sweden),Ki nevet a végén (Hungary),Parxís (Catalonia). Generally confused with other classic strategy board games like Pachisi, Parcheesi, Trouble, Sorry, & Aeroplane Chess, Ludo games are much easier to understand & play. So, get on board and start your Ludo games adventure with Ludo All Star right now, and be a Ludo star! Ludo All Star Highlights: * Regular & Arabic theme * Play online ludoo game in 2 player & 4 player modes * Play offline, Raid Mode, etc. * Undo your dice roll and be the lodo master of your own luck * Roll first after a 6, and then select tokens to apply the rolls to * Chat & make friends * Get lucky daily with a daily spin wheel * Earn coins by winning ludo games. Looking the more you win, the more you earn. Rules of Ludo Games Players take turns to roll the dice in lodo game. A player will have to roll a 6 before he or she is able to navigate a colored piece from its starting point to the starting square in lodoking. After that, in each of the subsequent turns the player navigates a piece forward for one to six squares as indicated by the dice roll. When a 6 is rolled, the player may choose to advance a token already in play lodo star online or may enter another staged token to its starting square. Rolling a 6 earns the player an additional or "bonus" roll in that turn. If the bonus roll results in a 6 again, the player earns an additional bonus roll in ledo games. If the third roll is also a 6, the player must forfeit his/her turn which then passes to the next player. When a piece has navigated the ledo board, it proceeds up the home column. A piece can only be moved onto the home pocket by an exact roll. The first player to move all 4 pieces into the home pocket wins. Get ready for the crazy adventure Ludo All Star is going to take you on, with it’s best ever in-game features. Online ludo multiplayer game is a cool lodu game that is playable both on your desktop and on Ludo Multiplayer is one of our selected ludu & lodu star game. Download Ludo All Star now! Master the lodoking game and be a Ludo Star! descriptionHTML:
Ludo is an online strategy board game for two to four players & dice game that will revive your childhood memories. Ludo is a board game played between friends, family & kids.

Ludo game, a simpler version of another Indian cross and circle game called Chopat, Chaupur, Pachisi or Parcheesi is a classic strategy board & dice game played by 2 or 4 players. Players roll a dice and race their four tokens from start to finish according to the dice roll.

Along with the usual gameplay, all new online ludo games, Ludo All Star has come up with an interesting twist that will make you a lodo king game.

The game also has a Raid Mode, which makes the lado star game more interesting.
Get ready for the toughest battle with the ludo Online game against three friends of you with the most classic board game.

Classic Ludo game is also going by different names & variations in different regions like लूडो,Uckers, Griniaris, Fia, Cờ cá ngựa, Petits Chevaux (Little Horses),Ki nevet a végén, برسي (Barjis/Barjees),Fei Xing Qi' (China),Parqués (Colombia),Barjis / Bargis (Palestine),Griniaris (Greece),Mens-erger-je-niet (the Netherlands),Parchís or Parkase (Spain),Le Jeu de Dada,Barjis(s) / Bargese (Syria),Pachîs (Persia/Iran),da' ngu'a ('Vietnam'),ludo chakka ( indian village),Parqués (Colombia),đá ngựa (Vietnam),Fei Xing Qi' (China),Parcheesi (North America),Parchís (Spain),Mensch ärgere Dich nicht (Germany),Non t'arrabbiare (Italy),Chińczyk (Poland),Reis ümber maailma (Estonia),Fia-spel or Fia med knuff (Sweden),Ki nevet a végén (Hungary),Parxís (Catalonia).

Generally confused with other classic strategy board games like Pachisi, Parcheesi, Trouble, Sorry, & Aeroplane Chess, Ludo games are much easier to understand & play. So, get on board and start your Ludo games adventure with Ludo All Star right now, and be a Ludo star!

Ludo All Star Highlights:
* Regular & Arabic theme
* Play online ludoo game in 2 player & 4 player modes
* Play offline, Raid Mode, etc.
* Undo your dice roll and be the lodo master of your own luck
* Roll first after a 6, and then select tokens to apply the rolls to
* Chat & make friends
* Get lucky daily with a daily spin wheel
* Earn coins by winning ludo games. Looking the more you win, the more you earn.

Rules of Ludo Games
Players take turns to roll the dice in lodo game. A player will have to roll a 6 before he or she is able to navigate a colored piece from its starting point to the starting square in lodoking. After that, in each of the subsequent turns the player navigates a piece forward for one to six squares as indicated by the dice roll.

When a 6 is rolled, the player may choose to advance a token already in play lodo star online or may enter another staged token to its starting square. Rolling a 6 earns the player an additional or "bonus" roll in that turn. If the bonus roll results in a 6 again, the player earns an additional bonus roll in ledo games. If the third roll is also a 6, the player must forfeit his/her turn which then passes to the next player.

When a piece has navigated the ledo board, it proceeds up the home column. A piece can only be moved onto the home pocket by an exact roll. The first player to move all 4 pieces into the home pocket wins.

Get ready for the crazy adventure Ludo All Star is going to take you on, with it’s best ever in-game features.
Online ludo multiplayer game is a cool lodu game that is playable both on your desktop and on Ludo Multiplayer is one of our selected ludu & lodu star game.
Download Ludo All Star now! Master the lodoking game and be a Ludo Star!

* Twitter: https://twitter.com/Ludoallstar
* Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ludoallstar/
* Website: https://www.ludoallstar.com/
* Blog: https://www.ludoallstar.com/blog

Check more on Wikipedia at https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ludo_(board_game)

description:
La app de Mercadona te da acceso a la compra online en tu supermercado de siempre. Si estás dentro de los códigos postales donde el servicio ya está disponible, puedes hacer la compra desde donde quieras con tu móvil de una forma rápida e intuitiva. Esta app te permite ver los productos en detalle, añadirlos a tu cesta, hacer la compra, revisar tus compras anteriores, modificar tus compras en función a tus necesidades y comprar tus productos habituales sin necesidad de listas.


Entre otras ventajas, el nuevo servicio de compra online ofrece:


- Horario extendido de entrega de 7:00 a 22:00 de lunes a sábado*.

- Tramos de 1 hora para que esperes el mínimo posible a tu compra.

- Máxima calidad y frescura garantizadas gracias a que recibimos tus productos frescos en el día y a la nueva flota de transporte con 3 temperaturas.

- Empleados propios de Mercadona que saben cómo dar el mejor trato a tus productos preparan y reparten tu compra desde el centro logístico correspondiente.

- Fotos de alta calidad de todos los productos.

- Consulta de la información nutricional, ingredientes y alérgenos consultando la imagen del producto con el zoom disponible para ello.

- Atención personalizada a través del chat con atención de 7:00 a 22:30 de lunes a sábado así como a través del teléfono gratuito de Atención al Cliente Mercadona 900 500 103.

*Horario de reparto los sábados sujeto a disponibilidad por zona geográfica a partir de las 17:00.

description:
Customise your shopping experience with the B&M app! Be first to hear about the latest offers and newest arrivals in-store. Create your own in-app shopping list to take with you to store and personalise your profile to make sure you’re the first to hear about the latest trends for the products you love.
 
With the B&M app you can:
 
Create your own profile and set your own shopping preferences for your favourite products

Use our handy Store Finder to find a B&M near you – save your nearest/favourite stores

Build your own shopping list to help you find your favourite products in-store

Get notifications about the things you love: new products, latest arrivals, promotions and offers, competitions, new stores and more!

Browse 1000s of products across all our full range, from Homeware, Furniture and Wallpaper to Toys, Electricals, Pets and much more!

Big Brands, Big Savings - discover new products from your favourite brands with our dedicated Brands page

title: Elisa Raamat
description:
Äpp on kõigile – pole vahet, kas oled Elisa või mõne teise mobiilioperaatori klient või elad hoopis näiteks välismaal. Kui Eesti isikukood on olemas, ei takista sind miski meie äppi kasutamast. Tutvumiseks kasuta kindlasti ka tasuta prooviaega, sest nii saad lugeda ja kuulata kõiki raamatuid 2 nädalat päris tasuta. Piiramatult.

Elisa Raamat on ainus äpp Eestis, kus saad lihtsalt ja mugavalt ühe soodsa kuutasu eest lugeda ja kuulata kogu e-raamatute valikut. Veelgi enam - ka populaarsemad ajakirjad on äpis olemas. Nii telefonis kui tahvlis, nii Eestis kui välismaal või kasvõi lennukis, sest netti pole lugemiseks vaja. Enam ei pea sa e-raamatuid ja ajakirju ükshaaval ostma. Ja mis peamine, lugemisvalik täieneb pidevalt.

title: Italia VR - Virtual Reality
description:
Italia Virtual Reality is the first app developed by ENIT – Italian National Tourist Board which allows you to discover the Italian beauties from a unique viewpoint: yours!
In this app you will find art, history, territory, culture, food and wine, and a bit of dolce vita, and you will have the chance to live authentic experiences, wherever you are.

Italia Virtual Reality is a project by ENIT – Italian National Tourist Board for an innovative promotion of our Country, focusing on the great UNESCO Heritage of Italy.

The app offers 3 immersive experiences, but will be continuously updated with new contents and you will be notifiedby push notifications.

You can choose between two viewing modes: 360 or VR, the VR requires the use of a virtual reality viewer attached to your smartphone. 
Install the app, choose a theme and then select an experience to live.

-------------------
Italy Virtual Reality is an innovative app and as such may not work properly on all devices. Make sure the phone is equipped with a gyroscope and accelerometer, characteristics essential for the proper functioning not only of the Italy Virtual Reality application, but also of all the virtual reality content that can be accessed via smartphones. These sensors allow the device to recognize even the smallest movements of the head and adapt the image accordingly, which otherwise appears still.
In any case, any functioning problem can be reported to redazione@enit.it.

title: DNA Live Taustakuvia
description:
"Tässä on paras uusi sovellus, DNA Live Taustakuvia, joka sopii kaikille tieteen ystäville, jotka haluavat tyylikäs ja houkutteleva design heidän älypuhelimissa. Sinun ehdottomasti rakastan näitä HD animoituja kuvia toisiinsa viestiketjut meillä geeneissä. Uskomaton kuviot DNA jättää sinut hengästynyt, varsinkin nyt, kun he tulevat eri uskomattomia värejä. Ole ensimmäisten joukossa ystäväsi on tämä ihmeellinen sisustus teidän matkapuhelimen näytön. Seuraa uusin trendi ja saada nämä Col tiede taustakuvia juuri nyt! Genetiikka ei ole koskaan ollut niin viileä, joten lataa uusi taustasovellus juuri nyt, ilmaiseksi!

- 3D Live taustakuva älypuhelimille
- HD DNA spinning ruudulla
- Sosiaalinen osake-painiketta ja lisää
- Uskomaton HD-grafiikka ja täysi tuki kotiin - näytön kytkentä ja vaaka-asennossa
- Motion valon ja vilkkuu muuttuu ajan
- On olemassa useita upeita DNA tausta teemoja odottaa sinua!

- DNA live tausta sopii täydellisesti sekä tablet-laitteisiin ja älypuhelimiin ja se tukee täysin vaakasuunnassa
- Tämä live taustakuva app on optimoitu akun käyttö ja se nukkumaan, kun puhelin ei ole käytössä, joten se ei kuluta akkua
- Yhteensopiva 99% matkapuhelimen ja tablet-laitteisiin
- Valitse suosikkisi taustakuvaksi ilmaiseksi!

Tutustu DNA Live Taustakuvia, paras uusi sovellus, joka tarjoaa sinulle upeita korkearesoluutioisia animoituja taustakuvia Samsung Galaxy ja Android ™. Amazing Droid DNA animaatioita vie sanattomaksi ja sinut koukussa uuden HD taustakuva kuvia. Marvelous valokuvat realistisia henkeäsalpaavan mikro maailma jättää sinut varma, onko se on vain kuva tai todellisuutta!

Uusi Droid DNA Taustakuva näyttää, miten uskomattoman elimistömme on hämmästyttävän HD kuvia mikro maailmaa sisällä meidän solut. Kuvia värikkäitä toisiinsa viestiketjut meidän geenien hämmästyttävän kirkkaat värit vie sanattomaksi. Vapaa DNA Live Taustakuvia sopii kaikille tieteen ystäville, jotka kaipaavat saada inspiraatiota ja etsivät loppiainen kokemus! Tämän ainutlaatuisen teräväpiirto DNA Live Taustakuvia voit nauttia kauniita kuvia viileä DNA lumoava sekoitus värejä, jotka luovat uskomattomia taideteoksia oikeassa, on kämmenelle. Olkoon nämä kuvat inspiroivat sinua ja sinut ymmärtämään, että se ei ole science fiction, mutta todellisuus, upouudet DNA HD kuvat! Monet eri taustakuvia antaa sinulle mahdollisuuden valita yksi, joka sopii sinulle parhaiten! Voit jakaa niitä ystävien ja yhdessä nauttia upeista värikkäitä maisemia. Se tulee olemaan unohtumaton kokemus, joten ota kaikki, että uusi DNA Live Taustakuvia on tarjota ja et tule katumaan sitä!

Hanki tämä upea taustakuvaksi, joka on aivan uusi markkinoilla, ja hemmotella itseäsi once in a lifetime kokemus ihana DNA tieteen kuvia joka antaa sinulle mahdollisuuden kurkistaa pienin osia soluja. Se on näky voitte vain kuvitella asti! DNA Taustakuva tekee sinut ymmärtämään, mitä on tehty, ja auttaa sinua ymmärtämään genetiikka hieman. Kaiken, mitä olet koskaan etsinyt vuonna tapetti on nyt täällä, vain kosketuksen päässä! Lataamalla tämän hämmästyttävän live taustakuva, saat parhaan paras, kun se tulee HD tieteen kuvia! DNA tarjoaa monia eri vaihtoehtoja ja se on jopa voit muokata Samsung Galaxy ja Android ™-laitteen.

DNA LWP on paras uusi app markkinoilla, joten purjehtia maailmassa tieteen ja genetiikan ja lataa tämän jäähtyä live taustakuva juuri nyt, täysin ilmaiseksi!


* Android ™ on tavaramerkki Google Inc.
* Tämä sovellus ei ole sidoksissa tai hyväksymässä Samsung."

title: Post-it®
description:
Post-it® App brings the simplicity of Post-it® Notes to your smartphone and tablet. Whether you use Post-it® Notes for collaboration, in education or for personal note taking, the Post-it® App helps you keep the momentum going.

Post-it® Notes, both analog and digital, are a great tool for organizing your thoughts, being creative and quickly reaching your goals. If you work from home or as a student in remote learning, use the Post-it® App to share your ideas with co-workers, structure your assignments and share them with your teacher, or create colorful calendars and share them with your friends.

Simply capture analog notes with your camera, or create new digital notes right on your device. Arrange, refine and organize ideas anyway you see fit. Then share your board with co-workers, teachers and friends, or export to your favorite apps and cloud services—including Trello, Dropbox, PowerPoint, Excel, PDF, and more.

Post-it® App features:

• Capture more than 200 individual square Post-it® Notes at a time with your camera.
• Get your notes transcribed using Handwriting Recognition. Great for search and exports.
• Draw, erase, type and change the color of your notes using powerful editing tools.
• Organize your way—group your ideas by thought or simply organize on a grid.
• Combine boards—collect and combine ideas from across multiple sessions.
• Share to your favorites formats and cloud services—supports Trello, Dropbox, PowerPoint, Excel, PDF, and more.

Learn more about the Post-it® App at post-it.com/app

Terms of Service: https://www.post-it.com/3M/en_US/post-it/ideas/app/eula/

title: VirtualSpeech - VR Courses
description: Practice soft skills in virtual reality with the VirtualSpeech app. Scenarios include public speaking, sales pitches, networking, presentations and media training. *app formerly known as Public Speaking for Cardboard / Public Speaking VR. Our app works with VR headsets, such as the Google Daydream, Google Cardboard, Blitzwolf VR and Merge VR. VR COURSES We offer a range of VR courses with additional VR scenarios and features. The courses combine traditional online classes with practice in VR. Current courses include: - Essential Public Speaking - Sales Pitch and Closing - Train the Trainer - Workplace Mindfulness - Business Networking - Learn English for Business - Leadership Communication - Business Storytelling - Many more courses covering a range of soft skills Visit our website to learn more and enroll onto these courses: Soft Skills Courses APP GUIDE Read about VR features, scenarios and setup in our App Guide. VR APP FEATURES - Speech Analysis: we provide real time feedback on elements such as hesitation words, pace of voice and eye contact. - Realistic VR Scenarios: selection of high quality rooms to improve your soft skills in, from communication to networking. - Track Your Progress: unlock awards, track speech analysis progress and listen back to your previous speeches. - Sound & Visual Distractions: audience and room distractions add to the immersion and make you feel like you’re at the event. - Add Your Own Slides: add your slides into the virtual room within the VR app, so that you can practice for an upcoming event. What is a VR headset? A VR headset is required when using this app. It is a device you wear over your eyes like a pair of goggles. It shows you an image on a high-definition screen in front of your eyes. The goal of the VR headset is to immerse you in the virtual environment.
descriptionHTML:
Practice soft skills in virtual reality with the VirtualSpeech app. Scenarios include public speaking, sales pitches, networking, presentations and media training.

*app formerly known as Public Speaking for Cardboard / Public Speaking VR.

Our app works with VR headsets, such as the Google Daydream, Google Cardboard, Blitzwolf VR and Merge VR.

VR COURSES
We offer a range of VR courses with additional VR scenarios and features. The courses combine traditional online classes with practice in VR. Current courses include:
- Essential Public Speaking
- Sales Pitch and Closing
- Train the Trainer
- Workplace Mindfulness
- Business Networking
- Learn English for Business
- Leadership Communication
- Business Storytelling
- Many more courses covering a range of soft skills

Visit our website to learn more and enroll onto these courses: Soft Skills Courses

APP GUIDE
Read about VR features, scenarios and setup in our App Guide.

VR APP FEATURES
- Speech Analysis: we provide real time feedback on elements such as hesitation words, pace of voice and eye contact.
- Realistic VR Scenarios: selection of high quality rooms to improve your soft skills in, from communication to networking.
- Track Your Progress: unlock awards, track speech analysis progress and listen back to your previous speeches.
- Sound & Visual Distractions: audience and room distractions add to the immersion and make you feel like you’re at the event.
- Add Your Own Slides: add your slides into the virtual room within the VR app, so that you can practice for an upcoming event.

What is a VR headset?
A VR headset is required when using this app. It is a device you wear over your eyes like a pair of goggles. It shows you an image on a high-definition screen in front of your eyes. The goal of the VR headset is to immerse you in the virtual environment.

title: DNApp - DNA/Protein Synthesis
description:
Have you ever wanted to learn about DNA and Protein Synthesis? Do you want interactive calculators for the processes of transcription and translation? Are you interested in supporting the work of students?

If you answered yes to any or all of the above, look no further! The DNApp was designed and written by students at Energy Institute High School as part of its Project-Based Learning curriculum. To answer the driving question, "How can we create an app to teach Biology students about DNA & genetics?" we turned to MIT App Inventor and worked to create an app that would do just that.

~~ FEATURES ~~

 - Definitions of some common vocabulary words!
 - Quizzes over said vocabulary words!
 - Diagrams of DNA, RNA, and a nucleotide that were totally not made in MS Paint!
 - A thrilling metaphor to describe the process of Protein Synthesis with accompanying illustrations that were also totally not made in MS Paint!
 - Calculators for transcription and translation (the two steps of Protein Synthesis) so that you don't have to decipher an mRNA codon chart yourself! Because that's boring.

DNApp
Everything you've ever wanted to know about DNA, probably

Credits: Kai Page, Adrian Fernandez, Isaac Sanchez, Danye Mitchell

If you are actually still looking at this, you deserve a cookie or something.

description:
Googlen VR-palvelut tarjoaa Daydream- ja Cardboard-sovellusten virtuaalitodellisuustoiminnot. Näitä ovat esimerkiksi ilmoitusten näyttäminen VR-tilassa, Daydream-yhteensopivien headsetien ja ‑ohjainten liittäminen pariksi Daydream-yhteensopivan puhelimen kanssa ja VR-sovellusten avaaminen ja niistä poistuminen.

title: Nordnet
description:
Käy kauppaa osakkeilla, rahastoilla ja muilla arvopapereilla helposti puhelimellasi. Lataa sovellus tänään ja laita rahasi kasvamaan!

Tarjoamme kaikki tarvitsemasi työkalut, palvelut ja tuotteet kaupankäyntiin ja markkinoiden seuraamiseen. Luo omia seurantalistoja, katso salkkusi kehitys ja tarkista toimeksiantojesi tila. Sovelluksen lataaminen ja käyttäminen on maksutonta.

Lisää fiksuja ominaisuuksia
- Kirjaudu sisään käyttäjätunnuksella ja salasanalla tai biometrisillä tunnisteilla (Fingerprint)
- Tutki osakkeita ja rahastoja ja käy niillä kauppaa
- Tarkista markkinalla olevat ja toteutuneet toimeksiantosi
- Tarkista omistuksesi ja salkkusi arvo. Voit nähdä myös salkkusi tai tietyn instrumentin kehityksen valitsemallasi ajanjaksolla.
- Luo omia seurantalistoja. Seurantalistat synkronoituvat automaattisesti sovelluksen uuden Nordnet.fi-palvelun kanssa.
- Lue uusimmat markkinatiedotteet ja omistuksiisi liittyvät uutiset.

Sovellus on maksuton
Katso Nordnetin tarjoamien palveluiden ja tuotteiden hinnat: https://www.nordnet.fi/palvelut-ja-tuotteet/hinnasto.html

Kun lataat sovelluksemme, hyväksyt samalla sen, että käytämme evästeitä. Näin käytämme evästeitä:
https://www.nordnet.fi/footer/evasteet.html

Palaute
Arvostamme palautettasi, koska sen avulla voimme kehittää sovellusta jatkuvasti paremmaksi. Arvostele sovellus ja anna palautetta kommenttiosiossa!

Turvallisuus
Kun olet kirjautuneena sisään, kaikki sovelluksen ja verkkopalvelumme välinen dataliikenne on salattu. Älä koskaan jätä puhelintasi, ilman että olet ensin kirjautunut ulos. Jos olet ollut passiivinen 60 minuuttia, sinut kirjataan automaattisesti ulos.

Yhteystiedot
Nordnet Bank AB Suomen sivuliike
Yliopistonkatu 5, 3. krs
FI-00100 HELSINKI

Puh: 020 198 5898
Sähköposti: asiakaspalvelu@nordnet.fi
www.nordnet.fi

Uutta sovelluksessa
Nordnet-sovellus on uudistunut täysin!
-Aiempaa parempi käyttäjäkokemus
- Uusia ominaisuuksia
- Aiemmin sovellusta haitanneita bugeja on korjattu

Tämä sovellus on koodattu alusta alkaen uudelleen. Jatkamme sovelluksen kehittämistä myös jatkossa. Lataa nyt uusin versio Nordnet-sovelluksesta ja aloita vaurastuminen!

title: Elisa - Face Painting Games
description:
We are so happy to present to you kids an awesome face paint game that brings a lot of features for your enjoyment. Elisa wants to get a new fancy makeover so she decides to go to the art studio for a face paint. This game is dedicated to all the girls and kids that like to paint, and it will bring you 4 unique mask patterns that will make Elisa beautiful. This face painting game starts with a simple scene where you kids need to choose one of the four mask that you want to apply on Elisa`s face.It does not matter if you choose a butterfly or other mask, I`m sure you will be able to create a master piece. After that you need to connect the red dots by clicking on then in the given sequence. After you complete this task the outline will become visible. You need to apply 4 colors on her face in the given spaces. You need to use the paint brush by moving it over the highlighted spaces. To complete the painting you need to apply a finishing touch with diamond dust. To make you art work more beautiful you can add items like flowers and shiny stars that you can move, resize and rotate the way you want. This fabulous step will make your face art unique. 
Elisa - Face Painting Games features : 
<<< four unique mask (two beautiful butterflies, two oriental pattern masks) >>>
<<< complete makeover after you finish the masks >>> 
<<< vibrant colors >>>
<<< easy to understand gameplay >>>
<<< 20+ amazing items to customize your art (flowers , stars, diamonds) >>> 
<<< cheerful ukulele music >>> 

Parents and kids are our best game testers and feedback providers, so if you have a minute to rate our app or give us your suggestions, we would love to hear it . You can also write to us at fizizi.com@gmail.com. 
Thank you for playing Elisa - Face Painting Games.

title: Telia Fleet Management Powered by Fleet Complete
description:
This app is only available for Telia Fleet Management customers. Please only download and install it if you have a valid account.

This app supports the features of Telia Fleet Tracker, Telia Equipment Tracker and Telia Mileage Logbook. For Telia Carsharing please download the app Telia Carsharing. 

Main features

Location tracking
- View vehicle's location and route history on map in real-time
	• Vehicle quick search
	• A selection of quality maps
	• Addresses are retrieved on demand
- Complete vehicle location info: address, coordinates, speed, heading

Personal driving score
- An overall safety and economy index, based on different diver behavior metrics, such as braking, accelerating, cornering, idling and driver's resting hours

Tracking
- Turn your handheld device into a portable tracker. You can create your own fleet by using mobile devices instead of dedicated GPS controllers. With this app, tablets and smartphones can be used as dedicated portable tracking devices. To do so, please register your devices by pressing 'Start Tracking' button in the home screen.

Task management
- Assign tasks directly from web application to field worker's smartphone or tablet
- Create and edit tasks on the fly
- View and manage customer-specific data
- Launch third-party navigation application
- Add photos and attachments to task
- View route to task location on map
- Signable data forms
	• Mileage calculation and reporting
	• Signable user-defined forms
	• Notifications and messaging
	• Photos
	• Travel time estimation

Asset management
- Pick up and drop QR coded assets
• Barcode scanner integration
